(284, 'The 43 Peculiarity', 3, '<p>Howard and Raj try to get to the bottom of why Sheldon disappears every afternoon at 2:45. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny deal with jealousy in their relationship.</p>', 8, 6, 30, '2012-11-15', '/img/4/12490.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(285, 'The Parking Spot Escalation', 3, '<p>When the University reassigns Sheldon\'s parking spot to Wolowitz, their fight affects the whole gang.</p>', 9, 6, 30, '2012-11-29', '/img/4/12491.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(286, 'The Fish Guts Displacement', 3, '<p>Sheldon tries to nurse a sick Amy back to health, while Wolowitz prepares for an upcoming fishing trip with his father-in-law.</p>', 10, 6, 30, '2012-12-06', '/img/4/12492.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(287, 'The Santa Simulation', 3, '<p>Sheldon revisits some Christmas memories during a game of Dungeons and Dragons, while Penny, Bernadette and Amy try to find a girl for Koothrappali when he joins the girls for ladies\' night.</p>', 11, 6, 30, '2012-12-13', '/img/4/12493.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(288, 'The Egg Salad Equivalency', 3, '<p>Sheldon gets accused of sexual harassment at the University and winds up getting Leonard, Raj and Wolowitz in trouble.</p>', 12, 6, 30, '2013-01-03', '/img/4/12494.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(289, 'The Bakersfield Expedition', 3, '<p>While the guys take a road trip to a comic book convention dressed as \"Star Trek: The Next Generation\" characters, the girls stay home and try to interpret a comic book.</p>', 13, 6, 30, '2013-01-10', '/img/4/12495.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(290, 'The Cooper/Kripke Inversion', 3, '<p>Sheldon is forced to work with Barry Kripke and faces a crisis of confidence. Meanwhile, Howard and Raj spend $1,000 on action figures of themselves.</p>', 14, 6, 30, '2013-01-31', '/img/4/12496.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(291, 'The Spoiler Alert Segmentation', 3, '<p>When Sheldon and Leonard fight, it affects Penny and Amy\'s living arrangements. Meanwhile, Raj takes care of Mrs. Wolowitz while Howard is away.</p>', 15, 6, 30, '2013-02-07', '/img/4/12497.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(292, 'The Tangible Affection Proof', 3, '<p>While the guys try to give their significant others the perfect Valentine\'s Day, Raj and Stuart throw a \"lonely people\" party at the comic book store.</p>', 16, 6, 30, '2013-02-14', '/img/4/12498.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(293, 'The Monster Isolation', 3, '<p>After a terrible date, Koothrappali vows to never leave his apartment. Meanwhile, Penny actually impresses Sheldon with her acting skills.</p>', 17, 6, 30, '2013-02-21', '/img/4/12499.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(294, 'The Contractual Obligation Implementation', 3, '<p>Leonard, Sheldon and Wolowitz speak to junior high girls about careers in science. Meanwhile, Koothrappali plans a date with Lucy.</p>', 18, 6, 30, '2013-03-07', '/img/5/12500.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(295, 'The Closet Reconfiguration', 3, '<p>Howard struggles with whether or not he should open a letter from his father, and Leonard and Penny throw a \"grown-up\" cocktail party at the apartment.</p>', 19, 6, 30, '2013-03-14', '/img/5/12501.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(296, 'The Tenure Turbulence', 3, '<p>Leonard, Sheldon and Raj fight for tenure at the University, and the competition heats up when the girls get involved.</p>', 20, 6, 30, '2013-04-04', '/img/5/12502.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(297, 'The Closure Alternative', 3, '<p>Sheldon feels lost after one of his favorite TV shows gets canceled too soon and Amy tries to help him get over his compulsive need for closure. Meanwhile, Raj discovers a secret about his new love interest, Lucy.</p>', 21, 6, 30, '2013-04-25', '/img/5/12503.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(298, 'The Proton Resurgence', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Leonard hire Professor Proton, the host of their favorite childhood TV show, to perform. Also, Howard and Bernadette run into trouble babysitting Raj\'s dog.</p>', 22, 6, 30, '2013-05-02', '/img/5/12504.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(299, 'The Love Spell Potential', 3, '<p>When the girls\' trip to Vegas falls through, the guys invite them to play Dungeons &amp; Dragons, causing Sheldon and Amy\'s relationship to take an unexpected turn. Meanwhile, Koothrappali and Lucy go on a very awkward date.</p>', 23, 6, 30, '2013-05-09', '/img/5/12505.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(300, 'The Bon Voyage Reaction', 3, '<p>New success for Leonard makes Sheldon very jealous and throws Penny for a loop. Meanwhile, Koothrappali pushes Lucy too far in their relationship.</p>', 24, 6, 30, '2013-05-16', '/img/5/12506.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(301, 'The Hofstadter Insufficiency', 3, '<p>With Leonard away, Sheldon and Penny spend quality time together sharing intimate secrets. Also, Wolowitz helps Raj get over his ex-girlfriend.</p>', 1, 7, 30, '2013-09-26', '/img/4/12100.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(302, 'The Deception Verification', 3, '<p>Leonard\'s friendship with Sheldon is put to the test when he returns from the North Sea. Meanwhile, Wolowitz\'s relationship with his mother causes an unusual threat to his masculinity.</p>', 2, 7, 30, '2013-09-26', '/img/4/12101.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(303, 'The Scavenger Vortex', 3, '<p>When the entire gang competes in a scavenger hunt designed by Raj, it brings out the best - and worst - in everyone.</p>', 3, 7, 30, '2013-10-03', '/img/4/12102.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(304, 'The Raiders Minimization', 3, '<p>Sheldon seeks revenge after Amy ruins one of his favorite movies. Meanwhile, Leonard discovers a way to get Penny to do anything, and Raj and Stuart create online dating profiles.</p>', 4, 7, 30, '2013-10-10', '/img/4/12103.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(305, 'The Workplace Proximity', 3, '<p>Sheldon must decide how much \"Amy time\" is too much after she takes a job at his university. Meanwhile, Howard finds himself sleeping on Raj\'s couch after a fight with Bernadette.</p>', 5, 7, 30, '2013-10-17', '/img/4/12104.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(306, 'The Romance Resonance', 3, '<p>Sheldon\'s major scientific breakthrough makes him feel like a fraud. Meanwhile, Howard\'s romantic gesture to Bernadette causes Penny to step up her game with Leonard.</p>', 6, 7, 30, '2013-10-24', '/img/4/12105.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(307, 'The Proton Displacement', 3, '<p>Sheldon feels slighted when Professor Proton seeks advice from Leonard instead of him, and he seeks revenge by befriending a rival science TV host, Bill Nye. Meanwhile, Raj gets jealous when Howard crashes \"girls\' night\".</p>', 7, 7, 30, '2013-11-07', '/img/4/12106.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(308, 'The Itchy Brain Simulation', 3, '<p>Leonard tries to keep Sheldon from overreacting when a past mistake comes to light, but Sheldon punishes Leonard by making him walk a mile in his shoes. Meanwhile, Penny confronts Raj\'s ex-girlfriend, Lucy.</p>', 8, 7, 30, '2013-11-14', '/img/4/12107.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(309, 'The Thanksgiving Decoupling', 3, '<p>Sheldon protests when the gang drags him to Mrs. Wolowitz\'s house for Thanksgiving. Meanwhile, Penny and Leonard must deal with a mistake from her past.</p>', 9, 7, 30, '2013-11-21', '/img/4/12108.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(310, 'The Discovery Dissipation', 3, '<p>Leonard and Amy help Sheldon cope with the shame he\'s feeling after his accidental contribution to science is disproved. Meanwhile, Raj must stay with Howard and Bernadette for a week.</p>', 10, 7, 30, '2013-12-05', '/img/4/12109.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(311, 'The Cooper Extraction', 3, '<p>While Sheldon is away in Texas, everyone gathers to decorate the apartment Christmas tree, and they each realize how much he has changed their lives.</p>', 11, 7, 30, '2013-12-12', '/img/4/12110.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `nom`, `serie_id`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `duree`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(312, 'The Hesitation Ramification', 3, '<p>When Penny\'s big acting break on NCIS is a bust, Leonard struggles to help her, which results in Penny asking Leonard a bold relationship question. Meanwhile, Sheldon tries to learn how to be funny and Raj tries to work on his \"game\" before talking to girls.</p>', 12, 7, 30, '2014-01-02', '/img/4/12111.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(313, 'The Occupation Recalibration', 3, '<p>Sheldon tries to relax after he is forced to take a vacation. Meanwhile, Leonard struggles to be supportive of Penny after she quits her job, and Bernadette seeks Stuart\'s help in replacing one of Howard\'s comic books.</p>', 13, 7, 30, '2014-01-09', '/img/4/12112.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(314, 'The Convention Conundrum', 3, '<p>After the guys can\'t get Comic-Con tickets, Sheldon tries to hold his own convention and winds up spending a wild night with James Earl Jones. Meanwhile, the girls see if they can act like \"grown-ups\".</p>', 14, 7, 30, '2014-01-30', '/img/4/12113.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(315, 'The Locomotive Manipulation', 3, '<p>Love is in the air when Sheldon and Amy join Howard and Bernadette for a trip to wine country. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny must rush Raj\'s dog to the vet.</p>', 15, 7, 30, '2014-02-06', '/img/4/12114.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(316, 'The Table Polarization', 3, '<p>Leonard buys a dining room table and it causes Sheldon to reevaluate the changes in his life. Meanwhile, Wolowitz is offered a chance to go back to space and Bernadette struggles with whether or not to encourage him.</p>', 16, 7, 30, '2014-02-27', '/img/4/12115.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(317, 'The Friendship Turbulence', 3, '<p>After the insults fly, Bernadette tries to broker the peace between Wolowitz and Sheldon. Meanwhile, Penny is offered an embarrassing movie role and Raj asks Amy to write to a woman on his behalf.</p>', 17, 7, 30, '2014-03-06', '/img/4/12116.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(318, 'The Mommy Observation', 3, '<p>When Sheldon visits his Mom in Houston, he is forced to confront a new reality. Meanwhile, Raj\'s \'Murder Mystery\' party starts some fights within the gang.</p>', 18, 7, 30, '2014-03-13', '/img/4/12117.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(319, 'The Indecision Amalgamation', 3, '<p>While Raj is wracked with guilt when he tries to date two women at once, Penny wrestles with whether to take a role in a cheesy movie and Sheldon is torn trying to choose between two gaming systems.</p>', 19, 7, 30, '2014-04-03', '/img/4/12118.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(320, 'The Relationship Diremption', 3, '<p>Sheldon faces a personal crisis after deciding he\'s wasting his time with string theory. Meanwhile, a double date between Raj, Emily and the Wolowitzes ends in embarrassment for Howard.</p>', 20, 7, 30, '2014-04-10', '/img/4/12119.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(321, 'The Anything Can Happen Recurrence', 3, '<p>When Sheldon tries to be spontaneous, it leads to unexpected friction between Penny, Amy and Bernadette. Meanwhile, Raj seeks Howard\'s help in preparing for a date with Emily.</p>', 21, 7, 30, '2014-04-24', '/img/4/12120.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(322, 'The Proton Transmogrification', 3, '<p>Professor Proton helps Sheldon cope with grief, while Leonard turns a relationship milestone into a competition with Penny. Meanwhile, Amy and Bernadette make a \"Star Wars Day\" gift for the guys.</p>', 22, 7, 30, '2014-05-01', '/img/4/12121.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(323, 'The Gorilla Dissolution', 3, '<p>Bad day causes Penny to reevaluate her life choices - including Leonard. Meanwhile, Howard and Bernadette struggle to care for Mrs. Wolowitz, and Raj gets relationship advice from Sheldon.</p>', 23, 7, 30, '2014-05-08', '/img/4/12122.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(324, 'The Status Quo Combustion', 3, '<p>Sheldon is forced to confront an uncertain future and considers a major move. Meanwhile, Raj and Emily take it to the next level, and Mrs. Wolowitz\'s injury is a major headache for Howard and Bernadette.</p>', 24, 7, 30, '2014-05-15', '/img/4/12123.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(325, 'The Locomotion Interruption', 3, '<p>Leonard and Amy take an unexpected road trip to Arizona to pick up Sheldon. Meanwhile, Penny interviews for a job at Bernadette\'s company, and Howard is weirded out by Stuart\'s relationship with Mrs. Wolowitz.</p>', 1, 8, 30, '2014-09-22', '/img/1/4498.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(326, 'The Junior Professor Solution', 3, '<p>Sheldon is ordered to teach a class, and the gang is surprised when Howard signs up to take it; and tensions between Penny and Bernadette afford Amy an opportunity to play one against the other.</p>', 2, 8, 30, '2014-09-22', '/img/1/4499.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(327, 'The First Pitch Insufficiency', 3, '<p>Wolowitz is nervous after NASA asks him to throw out the first pitch at a Los Angeles Angels game. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny try to prove Sheldon wrong after he says that he and Amy are a \"superior couple\".</p>', 3, 8, 30, '2014-09-29', '/img/1/4500.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(328, 'The Hook-Up Reverberation', 3, '<p>Raj\'s honesty about his past comes back to haunt him after his girlfriend, Emily, is cold to Penny. Also, the guys consider becoming part-owners in Stuart\'s comic book store.</p>', 4, 8, 30, '2014-10-06', '/img/1/4501.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(329, 'The Focus Attentuation', 3, '<p>Amy and Bernadette accuse Penny of being a \"buzzkill\" after she gets an email from work during their Vegas weekend. Meanwhile, the guys try to invent something cool, but only come up with new ways to procrastinate.</p>', 5, 8, 30, '2014-10-13', '/img/1/4502.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(330, 'The Expedition Approximation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Raj test whether they could survive a dark-matter research expedition in a salt mine by simulating the conditions in a steam tunnel. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny seek advice from Wolowitz and Bernadette after they fight about money.</p>', 6, 8, 30, '2014-10-20', '/img/1/4728.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(331, 'The Prom Equivalency', 3, '<p>When the gang recreates a high school prom on the roof the of the guys\' apartment building, Sheldon feels pressure to participate in all the typical romantic traditions.</p>', 8, 8, 30, '2014-11-06', '/img/3/8064.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(332, 'The Misinterpretation Agitation', 3, '<p>The guys try to help Penny out of an awkward work dilemma. Meanwhile, Amy and Bernadette argue over whether or not female scientists should play up their sexuality.</p>', 7, 8, 30, '2014-10-30', '/img/2/6683.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(333, 'The Septum Deviation', 3, '<p>When Leonard gets minor surgery on his nose, Sheldon is the one in need of sympathy. Meanwhile, Raj\'s parents\' impending divorce causes Howard and Bernadette to work on their own marriage.</p>', 9, 8, 30, '2014-11-13', '/img/4/10587.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(334, 'The Champagne Reflection', 3, '<p>Sheldon says a tearful goodbye to \"Fun with Flags.\" Also, Leonard, Howard and Raj look for something significant in a dead professor\'s research, and Bernadette is shocked to learn her co-workers\' true feelings from Penny.</p>', 10, 8, 30, '2014-11-20', '/img/8/21689.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(335, 'The Clean Room Infiltration', 3, '<p>On Christmas Eve, Amy plans a traditional Victorian dinner, while Raj, Leonard and Howard scramble to remove a pigeon that flew into the clean room at the university. To prove a point to Amy, a Scrooge-like Sheldon buys her the worst possible gift.</p>', 11, 8, 30, '2014-12-11', '/img/5/14957.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(336, 'The Space Probe Disintegration', 3, '<p>Wolowitz tries to distract Raj, who is anxiously awaiting data from a space probe he helped launch. Meanwhile, Sheldon and Leonard go dress shopping with Penny and Amy.</p>', 12, 8, 30, '2015-01-08', '/img/7/18901.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(337, 'The Anxiety Optimization', 3, '<p>The gang tries to help Sheldon when he becomes stuck in a rut at work by increasing his anxiety level. Howard teases Raj with a new game called \"Cinnamon or Emily?\"</p>', 13, 8, 30, '2015-01-29', '/img/8/20054.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(338, 'The Troll Manifestation', 3, '<p>After Leonard and Sheldon co-publish a physics paper, they must defend themselves against criticism from an online bully. Also, girls\' night finds Penny, Amy and Bernadette confronting embarrassing moments from their past.</p>', 14, 8, 30, '2015-02-05', '/img/8/20814.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(339, 'The Comic Book Store Regeneration', 3, '<p>Wolowitz receives some shocking news as everyone prepares for the reopening of Stuart\'s comic book store. Penny teaches Sheldon how to \"let it go,\" but can\'t follow her own advice after she learns something infuriating about Amy. Also, Leonard and Raj think they spot Nathan Fillion at a restaurant.</p>', 15, 8, 30, '2015-02-19', '/img/8/22003.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(340, 'The Intimacy Acceleration', 3, '<p>As a joke, Sheldon and Penny try an experiment designed to make participants fall in love. Also, Leonard, Amy, Raj and Emily spend the evening trying to escape a room with a \"zombie.\" And, after returning from Mrs. Wolowitz\' funeral, Bernadette and Howard run into trouble at the airport.</p>', 16, 8, 30, '2015-02-26', '/img/8/22442.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(341, 'The Colonization Application', 3, '<p>Trouble arises when Amy learns Sheldon has applied for a one-way mission to colonize Mars. Also, a trip to the pet store ends in a fight for Sheldon and Amy, Leonard surprises Penny with a very \"adult\" purchase, and, Raj is caught snooping in Emily\'s apartment.</p>', 17, 8, 30, '2015-03-05', '/img/9/23019.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(342, 'The Leftover Thermalization', 3, '<p>Friction ensues when a magazine fails to mention Leonard in an article about the paper he co-wrote with Sheldon. Also, a blackout at Mrs. Wolowitz\'s home leads to a final family dinner in her honor.</p>', 18, 8, 30, '2015-03-12', '/img/9/23725.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(343, 'The Skywalker Incursion', 3, '<p>When Leonard and Sheldon are invited to speak at UC Berkeley, they take a detour to try to meet an idol. Also, when Bernadette and Howard battle over the fate of his Dr. Who TARDIS, Raj and Amy offer to settle the dispute with a game of ping pong.</p>', 19, 8, 30, '2015-04-02', '/img/9/24939.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(344, 'The Fortification Implementation', 3, '<p>When Sheldon and Amy build a blanket fort, they come to major crossroads in their relationship. Also, Wolowitz meets the half-brother he never knew he had, and when Penny is invited to appear on Wil Wheaton\'s podcast, she and Leonard have a huge, on-air argument.</p>', 20, 8, 30, '2015-04-09', '/img/10/25283.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(345, 'The Communication Deterioration', 3, '<p>When Raj is asked to create a message in case a NASA mission discovers alien life, the guys fight over what he should do. Also, Penny is torn between auditioning for a movie or keeping her successful pharmaceutical sales job.</p>', 21, 8, 30, '2015-04-16', '/img/10/25898.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(346, 'The Graduation Transmission', 3, '<p>Wolowitz questions his engineering abilities when he and Sheldon can\'t get a toy drone to fly. Meanwhile, a cancelled flight nearly prevents Leonard from giving the commencement address at his former high school, and Raj pits his parents against each other when his father cuts him off financially.</p>', 22, 8, 30, '2015-04-23', '/img/10/26335.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(347, 'The Maternal Combustion', 3, '<p>Personalities collide when Sheldon and Leonard\'s mothers finally meet. Meanwhile, Howard finally decides to \"man up\" and do his fair share of the housework - but not without a little help from his friends.</p>', 23, 8, 30, '2015-04-30', '/img/10/26639.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(348, 'The Commitment Determination', 3, '<p>In the Season 8 finale, Leonard and Penny are pressured to set a wedding date by Sheldon, whose relationship with Amy has taken an interesting turn.</p>', 24, 8, 30, '2015-05-07', '/img/10/26990.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(349, 'The Matrimonial Momentum', 3, '<p>After driving to Vegas to get married, Penny struggles with Leonard\'s confession that he kissed another girl. Also, Sheldon doesn\'t know how to act after Amy pushes pause on their relationship.</p>', 1, 9, 30, '2015-09-21', '/img/19/49900.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(350, 'The Separation Oscillation', 3, '<p>Leonard confronts the woman he kissed on the North Sea in an attempt to set Penny\'s mind at ease. Also, Sheldon films a special episode of \"Fun with Flags\" after his breakup with Amy, and Bernadette feels guilty about withholding a secret from Penny.</p>', 2, 9, 30, '2015-09-28', '/img/21/54054.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(351, 'The Bachelor Party Corrosion', 3, '<p>The guys surprise Leonard with a belated bachelor-party weekend in Mexico, but their plans hit a bump in the road when they get a flat tire on the way. Meanwhile, the girls lean on Penny to tell her unsuspecting family that she and Leonard eloped.</p>', 3, 9, 30, '2015-10-05', '/img/22/57320.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(352, 'The 2003 Approximation', 3, '<p>Sheldon learns of an impending change in his living arrangements and decides to revert back to 2003, a simpler time before he met Leonard and Penny. Also, Howard and Raj form a band to play at the Comic Book Store.</p>', 4, 9, 30, '2015-10-12', '/img/24/60466.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(353, 'The Perspiration Implementation', 3, '<p>The guys take a fencing lesson from Barry Kripke and Sheldon finds himself in an awkward position when Kripke expresses interest in Amy. Also, when Stuart struggles to get female customers at the Comic Book Store, Penny, Amy and Bernadette come by to help him out.</p>', 5, 9, 30, '2015-10-19', '/img/25/63818.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(354, 'The Spock Resonance', 3, '<p>While being interviewed for a documentary about Spock from \"Star Trek\", Sheldon struggles to suppress his emotions about his recent break-up with Amy. Also, Wolowitz and Bernadette butt heads over remodeling his childhood home.</p>', 7, 9, 30, '2015-11-05', '/img/28/70784.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(355, 'The Helium Insufficiency', 3, '<p>In the midst of a nation-wide helium shortage, Sheldon and Leonard take desperate measures to get the supplies they need. Also, Penny and Bernadette download a dating app on Amy\'s phone to try and find her a new man.</p>', 6, 9, 30, '2015-10-26', '/img/26/66085.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(356, 'The Mystery Date Observation', 3, '<p>When Leonard, Penny and Bernadette learn that Amy is going out on a dinner date, the trio set out to spy on her and the guy. Meanwhile, Sheldon recruits Raj and Howard to find a woman for him, since they were responsible for getting Amy and him together.</p>', 8, 9, 30, '2015-11-12', '/img/29/74753.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(357, 'The Platonic Permutation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy try hanging out as friends when they spend Thanksgiving together at the aquarium. Also, Wolowitz reluctantly agrees to volunteer at the soup kitchen with Bernadette, Raj and Emily, and Penny discovers that Leonard knows more about her than she thought.</p>', 9, 9, 30, '2015-11-19', '/img/31/77852.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(358, 'The Earworm Reverberation', 3, '<p>Sheldon has a revelation when he realizes why a song was stuck in his head. Also, Amy invites Dave over for dinner despite their previously awkward date, and Wolowitz and Koothrappali become obsessed with a fan of their band, \"Footprints on the Moon\".</p>', 10, 9, 30, '2015-12-10', '/img/35/88078.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(359, 'The Opening Night Excitation', 3, '<p>As the guys prepare to go to the premiere of the new Star Wars movie, Sheldon plans a special event for Amy\'s birthday. Also, Leonard, Wolowitz, and Koothrappali must decide who will take their extra Star Wars movie ticket.</p>', 11, 9, 30, '2015-12-17', '/img/35/88073.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(360, 'The Sales Call Sublimation', 3, '<p>Penny gets more than she bargained for when Leonard agrees to meet with a psychiatrist on her behalf. Also, Sheldon and Koothrappali collaborate on an astronomical discovery, and Wolowitz and Bernadette can\'t believe what they are feeling after Stuart moves out.</p>', 12, 9, 30, '2016-01-07', '/img/38/95653.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(361, 'The Empathy Optimization', 3, '<p>After having to deal with a sick Sheldon, Leonard, Penny and the gang try to treat themselves to a Sheldon-free weekend.</p>', 13, 9, 30, '2016-01-14', '/img/39/99008.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(362, 'The Meemaw Materialization', 3, '<p>Sheldon\'s thrilled when his Meemaw comes to visit, but his excitement quickly fades when she butts heads with Amy. Also, Raj meets a new girl at the comic book store who makes him question his relationship with Emily.</p>', 14, 9, 30, '2016-02-04', '/img/42/105461.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(363, 'The Valentino Submergence', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy host a live Valentine\'s Day episode of Fun with Flags, Leonard and Penny grapple with getting older, Howard and Bernadette find a surprise in their hot tub and Raj is torn between Emily and the cute girl he met at the Comic Bookstore.</p>', 15, 9, 30, '2016-02-11', '/img/43/109341.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(364, 'The Positive Negative Reaction', 3, '<p>When the gang finds out about Bernadette\'s pregnancy, they celebrate by singing karaoke. Also, Bernadette is concerned when Wolowitz freaks out over her pregnancy announcement, and Wolowitz is convinced he must make more money to provide for the baby.</p>', 16, 9, 30, '2016-02-18', '/img/45/112735.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(365, 'The Celebration Experimentation', 3, '<p>After more than nine years together, the gang finally celebrates Sheldon\'s birthday, surprising him with a special guest.</p>', 17, 9, 30, '2016-02-25', '/img/45/114362.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(366, 'The Application Deterioration', 3, '<p>Leonard, Sheldon, and Wolowitz run into problems when they file for a patent for their infinite persistence gyroscope. Also, Penny, Amy and Bernadette give Koothrappali dating advice when Emily reaches out to him after their breakup.</p>', 18, 9, 30, '2016-03-10', '/img/47/118490.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(367, 'The Solder Excursion Diversion', 3, '<p>Amy is shocked at a revelation from Sheldon after she buys him a new laptop. Also, Koothrappali sells out Leonard and Wolowitz after they lie to their wives in order to attend an early screening of a movie.</p>', 19, 9, 30, '2016-03-31', '/img/50/126936.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(368, 'The Big Bear Precipitation', 3, '<p>Sheldon spills a secret of Leonard\'s when the two take a weekend cabin trip with Penny and Amy. Also, when Koothrappali goes overboard with pregnancy gifts, Wolowitz and Bernadette must draw the line.</p>', 20, 9, 30, '2016-04-07', '/img/52/130380.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(369, 'The Viewing Party Combustion', 3, '<p>Everyone must choose sides when a small argument between Leonard and Sheldon erupts into a heated fight during a group get-together.</p>', 21, 9, 30, '2016-04-21', '/img/55/137822.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(370, 'The Fermentation Bifurcation', 3, '<p>The gang goes to a wine bar and runs into Penny\'s old boyfriend, Zack. Also, Bernadette gets stuck spending the evening with Sheldon when she can\'t go wine tasting with the group, and things don\'t go as planned when Koothrappali introduces his new girlfriend, Claire.</p>', 22, 9, 30, '2016-04-28', '/img/55/137821.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(371, 'The Line Substitution Solution', 3, '<p>Sheldon hires Stuart to spend the day with Amy when he\'d rather go to a movie screening. Also, Leonard\'s mother, Beverly, comes to town and Penny struggles to make a connection with her.</p>', 23, 9, 30, '2016-05-05', '/img/56/140332.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(372, 'The Convergence Convergence', 3, '<p>Chaos ensues when Leonard\'s recently divorced parents, Alfred and Beverly, and Sheldon\'s devoutly religious mother, Mary, come to town. Also, Wolowitz and Koothrappali think the government is out to get them when they are contacted about their guidance system.</p>', 24, 9, 30, '2016-05-12', '/img/55/139271.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(373, 'The Conjugal Conjecture', 3, '<p>After Sheldon\'s mother and Leonard\'s father share an evening together, everyone deals with an awkward morning the following day. Also, Penny\'s family arrives for the ceremony, including her anxiety-ridden mother, Susan, and her drug dealing brother, Randall.</p>', 1, 10, 30, '2016-09-19', '/img/75/189808.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(374, 'The Military Miniaturization', 3, '<p>Colonel Williams, an Air Force representative from the Department of Material Command sits down to talk with Wolowitz.</p>', 2, 10, 30, '2016-09-26', '/img/75/189160.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(375, 'The Dependence Transcendence', 3, '<p>Tensions rise when the boys struggle to complete their government project on time and Sheldon tries an energy drink to stay awake. Also, Penny and Amy go to a \"party\" at Bert the geologist\'s house, and Kooothrappali learns Bernadette\'s true feelings about her pregnancy when they clean out the future baby room.</p>', 3, 10, 30, '2016-10-03', '/img/78/196809.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(376, 'The Cohabitation Experimentation', 3, '<p>When Amy\'s apartment floods, she proposes a \"cohabitation experiment\" with Sheldon. Also, Howard and Bernadette are upset when Koothrappali learns the gender of the baby before they do.</p>', 4, 10, 30, '2016-10-10', '/img/79/198605.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(377, 'The Hot Tub Contamination', 3, '<p>Leonard and Penny must separate a quarreling Sheldon and Amy when their cohabitation does not go as planned, and Sheldon threatens to break off their relationship when Amy refuses to adhere to the bathroom schedule. Also, Howard and Bernadette find unexpected guests at their house when they decide to stay home from a planned vacation.</p>', 5, 10, 30, '2016-10-17', '/img/80/201958.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(378, 'The Fetal Kick Catalyst', 3, '<p>Penny is surprised to learn she has fans of her performance in \"Serial Ape-ist\" when she attends Van Nuys Comic Con with Leonard. Also, Amy hosts a Sheldon-style brunch at Penny\'s apartment, and Wolowitz makes an impulsive purchase when he starts stressing out about the baby on the way.</p>', 6, 10, 30, '2016-10-27', '/img/82/207208.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(379, 'The Veracity Elasticity', 3, '<p>In order to continue living with Sheldon, Amy lies to him about repairs being made to her apartment and they host an \"on location\" episode of \"Fun With Flags\" in Penny\'s apartment. Also, Leonard lets Penny decorate Sheldon\'s old room after he learns that she has been secretly moving Leonard\'s collectibles into storage.</p>', 7, 10, 30, '2016-11-03', '/img/84/210793.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(380, 'The Brain Bowl Incubation', 3, '<p>After a successful experiment combining their genes, Sheldon will stop at nothing to convince Amy they should procreate. Also, Koothrappali is embarrassed to tell the gang what the new woman he\'s dating does for a living.</p>', 8, 10, 30, '2016-11-10', '/img/84/210794.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(381, 'The Geology Elevation', 3, '<p>When Bert, a Caltech geologist, wins the MacArthur Genius fellowship, Sheldon is overcome with jealousy. Also, Wolowitz finds an old remote control Stephen Hawking action figure he invented.</p>', 9, 10, 30, '2016-11-17', '/img/85/213120.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(382, 'The Property Division Collision', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Leonard must divide up their possessions and remove Penny\'s things from 4B.</p>', 10, 10, 30, '2016-12-01', '/img/89/223174.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(383, 'The Birthday Synchronicity', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy attempt to have an intimate moment together to celebrate Amy\'s birthday; Bernadette and Wolowitz welcome their newborn baby to the world.</p>', 11, 10, 30, '2016-12-15', '/img/89/223173.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(384, 'The Holiday Summation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy visit Leonard and Penny for the first time since the holidays and share details about their terrible trip to Texas.</p>', 12, 10, 30, '2017-01-05', '/img/92/230610.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(385, 'The Romance Recalibration', 3, '<p>Leonard and Penny ask for Sheldon\'s and Amy\'s help on putting the romance back in their marriage. Howard and Raj go to extreme lengths to stop the floor in Halley\'s bedroom from making noise.</p>', 13, 10, 30, '2017-01-19', '/img/94/235969.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(386, 'The Emotion Detection Automation', 3, '<p>Sheldon beta tests an MIT invention after hearing it can help him read people\'s emotions. Also, Leonard can\'t hide his feelings when Penny announces her brother is coming to town and Raj invites his ex-girlfriends over to give him dating advice.</p>', 14, 10, 30, '2017-02-02', '/img/96/241037.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(387, 'The Locomotion Reverberation', 3, '<p>Leonard and Wolowitz try to distract Sheldon when he slows the progress of their guidance system. Also, Penny and Amy take Bernadette out for the night, leaving Raj and Stuart to care for baby Halley.</p>', 15, 10, 30, '2017-02-09', '/img/97/243824.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(388, 'The Allowance Evaporation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy have their first fight since moving in together, and Koothrappali is shocked at the realities of financial independence when he stops receiving support from his father.</p>', 16, 10, 30, '2017-02-16', '/img/98/247215.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(389, 'The Comic-Con Conundrum', 3, '<p>With Koothrappali cut off from his father\'s fortune, he appoints Sheldon to help him get out of debt. Also, Penny considers joining Leonard at Comic-Con.</p>', 17, 10, 30, '2017-02-23', '/img/99/249435.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(390, 'The Escape Hatch Identification', 3, '<p>When Raj moves out of his apartment, Leonard and Penny offer him Sheldon\'s old room.</p>', 18, 10, 30, '2017-03-09', '/img/101/253767.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(391, 'The Collaboration Fluctuation', 3, '<p>Leonard, Penny and Raj adjust to their new living arrangement, and Sheldon takes an interest in Amy\'s work.</p>', 19, 10, 30, '2017-03-30', '/img/104/262432.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(392, 'The Recollection Dissipation', 3, '<p>Sheldon pushes himself to the limit when he collaborates on projects with Leonard and Wolowitz as well as Amy on the same day. Also, Bernadette is nearing the end of her maternity leave and must return to work.</p>', 20, 10, 30, '2017-04-06', '/img/105/264736.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(393, 'The Separation Agitation', 3, '<p>Howard and Bernadette have a hard time leaving Halley in day care when Bernadette returns to work. Also, Bert introduces the gang to his new girlfriend, Rebecca.</p>', 21, 10, 30, '2017-04-13', '/img/108/270249.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(394, 'The Cognition Regeneration', 3, '<p>Leonard isn\'t thrilled when Penny considers taking a new job offered by her ex-boyfriend, Zack.</p>', 22, 10, 30, '2017-04-27', '/img/109/273806.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(395, 'The Gyroscopic Collapse', 3, '<p>After Leonard, Sheldon and Wolowitz celebrate the completion of the top secret air force project, they are met with an unpleasant surprise. Also, Amy is offered a summer position as a visiting researcher.</p>', 23, 10, 30, '2017-05-04', '/img/110/276419.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(396, 'The Long Distance Dissonance', 3, '<p>The gang is concerned when Sheldon\'s former admirer, Dr. Ramona Nowitzki, resurfaces while Amy is away at Princeton.</p>', 24, 10, 30, '2017-05-11', '/img/111/278822.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(397, 'The Proposal Proposal', 3, '<p>Amy gives Sheldon an answer to his proposal while Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news.</p>', 1, 11, 30, '2017-09-25', '/img/142/355239.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(398, 'The Retraction Reaction', 3, '<p>Leonard angers the university – and the entire physics community – after he gives an embarrassing interview. Also, Amy and Bernadette bond over having to hide their success from Sheldon and Howard.</p>', 2, 11, 30, '2017-10-02', '/img/142/355242.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(399, 'The Relaxation Integration', 3, '<p>As Sheldon stresses about picking a wedding date, Amy tries to convince him he has a more laid-back side. Also, Koothrappali and Stuart compete to win the heart of Bernadette\'s new coworker, Ruchi.</p>', 3, 11, 30, '2017-10-09', '/img/142/355243.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(400, 'The Explosion Implosion', 3, '<p>Howard and Sheldon bond when they drive to the desert to shoot off a model rocket. Also, when Leonard\'s mom, Beverly, finds a new best friend in Penny, it rubs Leonard the wrong way.</p>', 4, 11, 30, '2017-10-16', '/img/131/329424.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(401, 'The Collaboration Contamination', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Koothrappali confide in Bernadette when they can\'t handle Amy and Wolowitz working together. Also, Penny and Leonard learn new tactics for how to deal Sheldon from an unlikely source.</p>', 5, 11, 30, '2017-10-23', '/img/132/331050.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(402, 'The Proton Regeneration', 3, '<p>Sheldon goes head-to-head with Wil Wheaton for the role of the new Professor Proton. Also, Penny steps in to take care of Halley when Bernadette and Wolowitz both wind up on bed rest.</p>', 6, 11, 30, '2017-11-02', '/img/132/332326.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(403, 'The Geology Methodology', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Bert collaborate on a research project, despite Sheldon\'s embarrassment. Also, Penny and Bernadette coach Koothrappali on how to navigate his relationship with Ruchi.</p>', 7, 11, 30, '2017-11-09', '/img/134/335924.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(404, 'The Tesla Recoil', 3, '<p>Leonard and Wolowitz are furious after they learn Sheldon went to work with the military behind their backs. Also, while Bernadette is on bed rest, she asks Raj to do some digging when she suspects Ruchi is trying to steal her job.</p>', 8, 11, 30, '2017-11-16', '/img/135/339330.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(405, 'The Bitcoin Entanglement', 3, '<p>Sheldon tries to teach the guys a lesson after they cut him out of a potentially valuable Bitcoin investment. Also, a seven-year-old video reveals a secret about Leonard and Penny\'s relationship.</p>', 9, 11, 30, '2017-11-30', '/img/136/342276.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(406, 'The Confidence Erosion', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy try to eliminate stress from wedding planning by applying math to the process. Also, Koothrappali \"breaks up\" with Wolowitz after realizing his best friend is actually hurting his confidence.</p>', 10, 11, 30, '2017-12-07', '/img/137/344140.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(407, 'The Celebration Reverberation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Wolowitz plan birthday celebrations for Amy and Halley, respectively. Also, Leonard receives a Christmas letter from his brother that causes him to spiral out about his own lack of accomplishments.</p>', 11, 11, 30, '2017-12-14', '/img/138/346472.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(408, 'The Matrimonial Metric', 3, '<p>To discover who would be most qualified to be best man and maid of honor at their wedding, Sheldon and Amy subject their friends to a series of secret experiments. Also, Penny reveals her true feelings about Amy.</p>', 12, 11, 30, '2018-01-04', '/img/141/352926.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(409, 'The Solo Oscillation', 3, '<p>When Sheldon kicks Amy out to work solo, she and Leonard bond during a series of science experiments. Also, Bert the geologist replaces Wolowitz in the band Footprints on the Moon, and Sheldon finds Penny a surprising source of scientific inspiration.</p>', 13, 11, 30, '2018-01-11', '/img/142/355438.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(410, 'The Separation Triangulation', 3, '<p>Koothrappali finds himself in the middle of domestic drama when he learns the woman he\'s dating, Nell, has a very upset husband, Oliver. Also, when Sheldon rents his old room back for a quiet place to work, he drives Leonard crazy by being a model tenant.</p>', 14, 11, 30, '2018-01-18', '/img/142/356979.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(411, 'The Novelization Correlation', 3, '<p> When Sheldon petitions Wil Wheaton to appear on the new Professor Proton show, Wil offers a role to Amy instead. Also, Penny gets angry when she thinks the female protagonist in Leonard\'s novel is based on her.</p>', 15, 11, 30, '2018-02-01', '/img/144/361596.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(412, 'The Neonatal Nomenclature', 3, '<p>When Bernadette won\'t go into labor, all her friends try different tactics to get things started. Also, Wolowitz confronts Bernadette after Amy accidentally reveals she\'s already chosen their son\'s name.</p>', 16, 11, 30, '2018-03-01', '/img/147/368495.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(413, 'The Athenaeum Allocation', 3, '<p>Leonard jumps through hoops to help secure the perfect wedding venue for Sheldon and Amy. Also, Bernadette and Wolowitz have a hard time deciding who should stay at home with the kids and who should go back to work.</p>', 17, 11, 30, '2018-03-08', '/img/148/371530.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(414, 'The Gates Excitation', 3, '<p>Penny gets the opportunity to host Bill Gates at work when his company wants to partner with her pharmaceutical company. Also, Leonard, Koothrappali and Wolowitz do everything in their power to meet him, while Sheldon thinks he is the victim of an April Fools prank.</p>', 18, 11, 30, '2018-03-29', '/img/151/379315.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(415, 'The Tenant Disassociation', 3, '<p>When Leonard learns Sheldon is the president of the tenants association, he decides to run against him. Also, Bernadette encourages Wolowitz and Koothrappali to find the owner of a drone after they find it in the backyard.</p>', 19, 11, 30, '2018-04-05', '/img/151/379314.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(416, 'The Reclusive Potential', 3, '<p>A brilliant but reclusive scientist, Doctor Wolcott, invites Sheldon to his cabin in the middle of nowhere, and Leonard, Raj and Howard go along for the trip. Also, Penny and Bernadette improvise after Amy doesn\'t like the tame bachelorette party they planned for her.</p>', 20, 11, 30, '2018-04-12', '/img/152/381194.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(417, 'The Comet Polarization', 3, '<p>Sheldon\'s comic book store experiences changes when writer Neil Gaiman puts Stuart\'s store on the map. Also, Koothrappali takes credit for Penny\'s astronomical discovery, and friendships are threatened.</p>', 21, 11, 30, '2018-04-19', '/img/153/382793.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(418, 'The Monetary Insufficiency', 3, '<p>Sheldon goes to Vegas to win money for science. Also, Penny and Bernadette take Amy wedding dress shopping, but her terrible choice entangles them in a web of lies.</p>', 22, 11, 30, '2018-04-26', '/img/154/386157.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(419, 'The Sibling Realignment', 3, '<p>When Sheldon learns that his mother won\'t attend his wedding unless he invites his brother, Georgie, he and Leonard travel to Texas to end a family feud. Also, the Wolowitz kids inadvertently infest Amy, Bernadette, Wolowitz and Koothrappali with pinkeye.</p>', 23, 11, 30, '2018-05-03', '/img/154/386385.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(420, 'The Bow Tie Asymmetry', 3, '<p>Amy and Sheldon\'s wedding provides Sheldon with the information he needs to make a breakthrough in his symmetrical string theory. Meanwhile, their friends pick up Sheldon and Amy\'s families from the airport, and Mark Hamill agrees to officiate at the ceremony.</p>', 24, 11, 30, '2018-05-10', '/img/155/388166.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(421, 'The Conjugal Configuration', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy\'s honeymoon runs aground in New York, while Penny and Leonard discover they are uncomfortably similar to Amy\'s parents, Mr. and Mrs. Fowler. Also, Koothrappali insults physicist Neil deGrasse Tyson and starts a Twitter war.</p>', 1, 12, 30, '2018-09-24', '/img/170/425575.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(422, 'The Wedding Gift Wormhole', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy drive themselves crazy trying to figure out what \"perfect gift\" Leonard and Penny gave them for their wedding. Also, Koothrappali decides he wants to settle down and asks his father to arrange a marriage for him.</p>', 2, 12, 30, '2018-09-27', '/img/170/425574.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(423, 'The Tam Turbulence', 3, '<p>When Sheldon won\'t tell anyone why he\'s never mentioned Tam, his childhood best friend, Leonard takes matters into his own hands. Also, Bernadette and Penny take out Raj\'s fiancée, Anu, for dinner to get the skinny on her.</p>', 4, 12, 30, '2018-10-11', '/img/171/428314.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(424, 'The Procreation Calculation', 3, '<p>The Wolowitzes\' life gets complicated when Stuart starts bringing his new girlfriend home. Also, Penny and Leonard talk about starting a family while Koothrappali explores an arranged marriage.</p>', 3, 12, 30, '2018-10-04', '/img/170/425573.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(425, 'The Planetarium Collision', 3, '<p>When Amy doesn\'t have time to work on super-asymmetry, Sheldon goes to great lengths to ensure she\'s available to work with him even it if means accidentally sabotaging her career in the process. Also, Koothrappali doesn\'t want Wolowitz to join him in hosting a show at the planetarium.</p>', 5, 12, 30, '2018-10-18', '/img/171/429994.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(426, 'The Imitation Perturbation', 3, '<p>When Wolowitz dresses up as Sheldon for Halloween, Sheldon seeks retaliation at Leonard and Penny\'s Halloween party. Also, Leonard is shocked that Penny doesn\'t remember their first kiss.</p>', 6, 12, 30, '2018-10-25', '/img/172/431129.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(427, 'The Grant Allocation Derivation', 3, '<p>Leonard is caught between a rock and a hard place when he\'s responsible for distributing extra grant money. Also, Bernadette turns the backyard playhouse into a hideaway from her husband and kids.</p>', 7, 12, 30, '2018-11-01', '/img/173/433874.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(428, 'The Consummation Deviation', 3, '<p>Sheldon tries to bond with Amy\'s father, but when Wolowitz lures Mr. Fowler away with magic tricks, Sheldon has no choice but to bond with Mrs. Fowler. Also, Koothrappali and Anu try to get physical for the first time.</p>', 8, 12, 30, '2018-11-08', '/img/174/435544.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(429, 'The Citation Negation', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy are devastated after learning from a Russian paper that Super Asymmetry has already been discovered and disproven. Also, ultra-competitive Bernadette asks Stuart\'s girlfriend, Denise, to teach her how to beat Howard in a popular videogame.</p>', 9, 12, 30, '2018-11-15', '/img/174/435847.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(430, 'The VCR Illumination', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy are still down about their theory being disproven, but a VHS tape from Sheldon\'s past inspires him not to give up. Also, Bernadette turns into a pageant mom when she tries to help Wolowitz ace his Magic Castle audition.</p>', 10, 12, 30, '2018-12-06', '/img/176/441718.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(431, 'The Paintball Scattering', 3, '<p>Penny and Leonard organize a paintball game that results in mayhem when Sheldon is jealous of Amy. Also, Koothrappali catches Anu with her ex-boyfriend, and Stuart doesn\'t want to move in with Denise.</p>', 11, 12, 30, '2019-01-03', '/img/179/447871.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(432, 'The Propagation Proposition', 3, '<p>Penny\'s ex-boyfriend, Zack, and his wife want a baby, but when Zack is infertile, they ask Leonard for help. Also, Koothrappali attempts to mend things with his ex-fiancée, Anu.</p>', 12, 12, 30, '2019-01-10', '/img/179/449443.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(433, 'The Confirmation Polarization', 3, '<p>When Sheldon and Amy\'s super asymmetry theory is proven by two physicists, Dr. Pemberton and Dr. Campbell from Chicago, they\'re thrilled, until they try to kick Amy off the Nobel nomination. Also, Bernadette has a big success at work and Penny\'s going to be a part of it – whether she wants to or not.</p>', 13, 12, 30, '2019-01-17', '/img/180/450967.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(434, 'The Meteorite Manifestation', 3, '<p>Sheldon is thrilled to help Bernadette and Wolowitz navigate bureaucratic paperwork, until he discovers they are breaking the law. Also, Leonard is disappointed when his friends exclude him from a scientific project.</p>', 14, 12, 30, '2019-01-31', '/img/182/455458.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(435, 'The Donation Oscillation', 3, '<p>Penny tries to seduce an abstaining Leonard to ruin his \"donation\" for her ex-boyfriend, Zack, and his wife, Marissa. Also, Wolowitz, Bernadette, Anu and Koothrappali turn Koothrappali\'s canceled bachelor party into a couple\'s trip aboard the \"vomit comet,\".</p>', 15, 12, 30, '2019-02-07', '/img/182/457473.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(436, 'The D & D Vortex', 3, '<p>When the gang finds out Wil Wheaton hosts a celebrity Dungeons and Dragons game involving William Shatner, Joe Manganiello, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar and Kevin Smith, deception and betrayal are the path to make it to the one open seat.</p>', 16, 12, 30, '2019-02-21', '/img/184/462416.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(437, 'The Conference Valuation', 3, '<p>When Penny and Bernadette go to San Diego for a pharmaceutical sales convention, Wolowitz is in charge of the kids. Also, Sheldon finds a book on experimenting on kids, and the guys plus Amy make a day of it.</p>', 17, 12, 30, '2019-03-07', '/img/186/467456.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(438, 'The Laureate Accumulation', 3, '<p>When competitors Pemberton and Campbell charm America on a publicity tour, Sheldon and Amy try to bring Nobel laureates Kip Thorne, George Smoot and Frances Arnold to their side. Also, Halley\'s fear of the dark leads to opportunity and conflict for Howard, Bernadette and Stuart.</p>', 18, 12, 30, '2019-04-04', '/img/190/476575.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(439, 'The Inspiration Deprivation', 3, '<p>The concept of what it would mean for women everywhere if Amy were to win a Nobel Prize causes Amy to have a meltdown. Also, Koothrappali and Wolowitz try to relive the good old days after Wolowitz buys a scooter that looks like the one he had years ago.</p>', 19, 12, 30, '2019-04-18', '/img/192/480675.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(440, 'The Decision Reverberation', 3, '<p>Koothrappali is worried people won\'t take him seriously in his own field after publishing a paper that suggests he may have discovered alien life. Also, Leonard wants to be the principal investigator on a plasma physics study.</p>', 20, 12, 30, '2019-04-25', '/img/193/483551.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(441, 'The Plagiarism Schism', 3, '<p>Kripke has proof that Dr. Pemberton plagiarized his thesis in college, and Sheldon and Amy aren\'t sure if they should turn him in or not. Also, Wolowitz is happily surprised to learn that Bernadette wasn\'t the only waitress at the Cheesecake Factory who had a crush on him back in the day.</p>', 21, 12, 30, '2019-05-02', '/img/194/485926.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(442, 'The Maternal Conclusion', 3, '<p>Leonard is pleasantly surprised when Beverly comes to visit and she\'s genuinely kind to him, until he finds out the real reason she\'s there. Also, Denise and Stuart overstay their welcome at the Wolowitz house.</p>', 22, 12, 30, '2019-05-09', '/img/195/489825.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(443, 'The Change Constant', 3, '<p>Sheldon and Amy await big news.</p>', 23, 12, 30, '2019-05-16', '/img/197/493238.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(444, 'The Stockholm Syndrome', 3, '<p>Bernadette and Wolowitz leave their kids for the first time; Penny and Leonard try to keep a secret; Sheldon and Amy stick together; and Koothrappali makes a new friend, as the gang travels together into an uncharted future.</p>', 24, 12, 30, '2019-05-16', '/img/197/493243.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(445, 'Days Gone Bye', 4, '<p>Rick searches for his family after emerging from a coma into a world terrorized by the walking dead. Morgan and Duane, whom he meets along the way, help teach Rick the new rules for survival.</p>', 1, 1, 60, '2010-10-31', '/img/0/2104.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(446, 'Guts', 4, '<p>Rick unknowingly causes a group of survivors to be trapped by walkers. The group dynamic devolves from accusations to violence, as Rick must confront an enemy far more dangerous than the undead.</p>', 2, 1, 60, '2010-11-07', '/img/1/3424.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(447, 'Tell It to the Frogs', 4, '<p>Rick makes a decision to go back to Atlanta to retrieve the bag of guns and save a man\'s life. Lori and Shane must deal with the surprising return of someone they thought was dead.</p>', 3, 1, 60, '2010-11-14', '/img/1/3425.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(448, 'Vatos', 4, '<p>Rick\'s mission to Atlanta is jeopardized when things go awry. Jim becomes unhinged in camp.</p>', 4, 1, 60, '2010-11-21', '/img/1/3426.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(449, 'Wildfire', 4, '<p>Rick leads the group to the CDC after the attack. Jim must make a terrible life and death decision</p>', 5, 1, 60, '2010-11-28', '/img/1/3427.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(450, 'TS-19', 4, '<p>Rick and the group are allowed into the CDC by a strange doctor. But all is not what it seems in their newfound haven.</p>', 6, 1, 60, '2010-12-05', '/img/1/3428.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(451, 'What Lies Ahead', 4, '<p>After the CDC explosion, the survivors are still on the move when they encounter a herd of walkers that separates one of their own, leading them to a possible safe haven.</p>', 1, 2, 60, '2011-10-16', '/img/1/3429.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(452, 'Bloodletting', 4, '<p>Coming to the aid of another, Rick discovers a possible safe haven. Shane must go on a dangerous mission to get badly needed medical supplies.</p>', 2, 2, 60, '2011-10-23', '/img/1/3430.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(453, 'Save the Last One', 4, '<p>The group desperately awaits Shane\'s return. Shane finds himself trapped in a school, surrounded by the undead. Daryl and Andrea search for someone in the woods.</p>', 3, 2, 60, '2011-10-30', '/img/1/3431.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(454, 'Cherokee Rose', 4, '<p>Shane makes a deadly sacrifice which leads to unusual behavior and self-distancing. The rest of the group tries to hang on somewhere between living to die and dying to live.</p>', 4, 2, 60, '2011-11-06', '/img/1/3432.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `nom`, `serie_id`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `duree`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(455, 'Chupacabra', 4, '<p>Glenn, the only one breaking barriers between both groups, knows far too much for his comfort level. Daryl finds a sign of life and, in his delirium, tries to make it back to the farm alive.</p>', 5, 2, 60, '2011-11-13', '/img/1/3433.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(456, 'Secrets', 4, '<p>Secrets are told and secrets are revealed. Hershel refuses to acknowledge the world’s new reality. Andrea comes out of her shell. Everyone is becoming more and more aware that “everything is food for something.”</p>', 6, 2, 60, '2011-11-20', '/img/1/3434.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(457, 'Pretty Much Dead Already', 4, '<p>Hershel sets a deadline. All secrets are out in the open. Glenn stands up for himself and Shane takes charge.</p>', 7, 2, 60, '2011-11-27', '/img/1/3435.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(458, 'Nebraska', 4, '<p>Rick and the others try to restore order in the aftermath of a terrible discovery. Hershel takes up an old habit and disappears, Rick and Glenn must follow him into town.</p>', 8, 2, 60, '2012-02-12', '/img/1/3436.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(459, 'Triggerfinger', 4, '<p>Trapped, Rick, Hershel and Glenn fight to survive against new foes, both dead and alive. Shane finds Lori in danger on the road and makes it his mission to bring her back to the farm.</p>', 9, 2, 60, '2012-02-19', '/img/1/3437.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(460, '18 Miles Out', 4, '<p>Rick and Shane come into conflict over the fate of an outsider. Andrea helps Hershel\'s youngest daughter face a crucial decision.</p>', 10, 2, 60, '2012-02-26', '/img/1/3438.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(461, 'Judge, Jury, Executioner', 4, '<p>Rick sides with Shane on an important decision, causing Dale to worry that the group is losing its humanity. Carl\'s actions have unintended consequences on the group.</p>', 11, 2, 60, '2012-03-04', '/img/1/3439.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(462, 'Better Angels', 4, '<p>The group learns that someone dangerous may be on the loose near the farm. As night falls, Rick, Shane, Daryl and Glenn comb the woods to handle the situation and keep the group safe.</p>', 12, 2, 60, '2012-03-11', '/img/1/3441.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(463, 'Beside the Dying Fire', 4, '<p>Rick and Carl return from the woods to find the farm in jeopardy. The group is split up in the ensuing chaos. With things looking grim, Rick’s leadership is questioned.</p>', 13, 2, 60, '2012-03-18', '/img/1/3443.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(464, 'Seed', 4, '<p>With the world growing increasingly more dangerous and Lori’s pregnancy advancing, Rick discovers a potentially safe haven. But first he must secure the premises, pushing his group to its limit.</p>', 1, 3, 60, '2012-10-14', '/img/1/3444.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(465, 'Sick', 4, '<p>After a traumatic event, a life hangs in the balance. Complicating matters, the group must also deal with a potential threat to their new surroundings.</p>', 2, 3, 60, '2012-10-21', '/img/1/3446.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(466, 'Walk with Me', 4, '<p>After witnessing an accident, Andrea and Michonne are introduced to a new community of survivors. As conflicts arise with their new acquaintances, a decision must be made.</p>', 3, 3, 60, '2012-10-28', '/img/1/3448.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:00', '2019-12-19 02:15:00'),
(467, 'Killer Within', 4, '<p>The group is severed and lives are put in jeopardy. In Woodbury, Merle has a request for the Governor.</p>', 4, 3, 60, '2012-11-04', '/img/1/3449.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(468, 'Say the Word', 4, '<p>After another loss, Rick struggles. Michonne remains suspicious of the Governor as he throws a party with a unique twist for the people of Woodbury.</p>', 5, 3, 60, '2012-11-11', '/img/1/3450.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(469, 'Hounded', 4, '<p>As Andrea grows closer to the Governor, Michonne makes a decision about Woodbury. Glenn and Maggie go on a run. Rick struggles.</p>', 6, 3, 60, '2012-11-18', '/img/1/3451.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(470, 'When the Dead Come Knocking', 4, '<p>The Governor presses for information. A new guest arrives at the prison, forcing Rick\'s hand.</p>', 7, 3, 60, '2012-11-25', '/img/1/3453.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(471, 'Made to Suffer', 4, '<p>Andrea steps up as the people of Woodbury are thrown into uncharted territory. At the prison, a new threat arises.</p>', 8, 3, 60, '2012-12-02', '/img/1/3456.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(472, 'The Suicide King', 4, '<p>Rick tries to rescue a member of his group. Woodbury is in disarray after a recent attack. New guests raise concerns at the prison.</p>', 9, 3, 60, '2013-02-10', '/img/1/3458.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(473, 'Home', 4, '<p>As the group debates their next course of action, Rick wanders after a lost friend. Daryl and Merle question their choices. The Governor restores order in Woodbury and makes plans to punish those responsible.</p>', 10, 3, 60, '2013-02-17', '/img/1/3459.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(474, 'I Ain\'t a Judas', 4, '<p>Their security threatened, Rick and the group must make a choice. With Woodbury in a police state, Andrea grows uneasy.</p>', 11, 3, 60, '2013-02-24', '/img/1/3461.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(475, 'Clear', 4, '<p>Realizing they are heavily outgunned against the Governor\'s forces, Rick leads an expedition to get more weapons.</p>', 12, 3, 60, '2013-03-03', '/img/1/3462.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(476, 'Arrow on the Doorpost', 4, '<p>In an effort to prevent any more deaths, Rick and the Governor meet to come up with a peace treaty.</p>', 13, 3, 60, '2013-03-10', '/img/1/3463.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(477, 'Prey', 4, '<p>The Governor chases a dissenter who fled Woodbury. While the Governor is gone, a traitor tries to sabotage his upcoming plans.</p>', 14, 3, 60, '2013-03-17', '/img/1/3465.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(478, 'This Sorrowful Life', 4, '<p>Rick and the group are faced with a serious problem. If they want a truce with the Governor, they will have to make a huge sacrifice.</p>', 15, 3, 60, '2013-03-24', '/img/1/3466.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(479, 'Welcome to the Tombs', 4, '<p>Rick and the group have to seriously consider if the prison is worth defending as the Governor\'s impending attack looms over their heads.</p>', 16, 3, 60, '2013-03-31', '/img/1/3467.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(480, '30 Days Without an Accident', 4, '<p>Rick and the group are as close to an ideal life as possible at the prison. Will they be able to hold on to humanity in the face of a new evil?</p>', 1, 4, 60, '2013-10-13', '/img/1/3468.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(481, 'Infected', 4, '<p>As the group faces a brand new enemy, Rick and the others must fight to protect the livelihood they worked so hard to create at the prison.</p>', 2, 4, 60, '2013-10-20', '/img/1/3469.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(482, 'Isolation', 4, '<p>As one group leaves the prison in search for supplies at a local college, those who stay must deal with recent losses while preserving what remains.</p>', 3, 4, 60, '2013-10-27', '/img/1/3470.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(483, 'Indifference', 4, '<p>While on a supplies mission to a local college, members of the group run into multiple hurdles. Things at the prison are getting worse.</p>', 4, 4, 60, '2013-11-03', '/img/1/3471.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(484, 'Internment', 4, '<p>Multiple enemies put pressure on Rick and the group. Could this finally be the breaking point for the survivors and the prison?</p>', 5, 4, 60, '2013-11-10', '/img/1/3472.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(485, 'Live Bait', 4, '<p>A familiar face returns as each member of the group struggles to find his or her humanity in a world of constant threats.</p>', 6, 4, 60, '2013-11-17', '/img/1/3473.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(486, 'Dead Weight', 4, '<p>A new and scary chapter is unfolding at a camp outside the prison. Will peace be attainable with the addition of new members?</p>', 7, 4, 60, '2013-11-24', '/img/1/3474.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(487, 'Too Far Gone', 4, '<p>Just when everything started to calm down at the prison, Rick and his group now face imminent danger and destruction. This time, they might not win.</p>', 8, 4, 60, '2013-12-01', '/img/1/3475.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(488, 'After', 4, '<p>As Rick deals with old wounds, members of the prison have to come to terms with their new environment and ask themselves if survival alone is enough.</p>', 9, 4, 60, '2014-02-09', '/img/1/3476.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(489, 'Inmates', 4, '<p>The group encounters many obstacles in their quest to find stability and safety, but sometimes all they have to guide them is hope.</p>', 10, 4, 60, '2014-02-16', '/img/1/3477.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(490, 'Claimed', 4, '<p>The group encounters many obstacles in their quest to find stability and safety, but sometimes all they have to guide them is hope.</p>', 11, 4, 60, '2014-02-23', '/img/1/3478.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(491, 'Still', 4, '<p>Faced with the day-to-day survival of life outside shelter, a simple request by someone in the group leads to a bizarre but enlightening mission.</p>', 12, 4, 60, '2014-03-02', '/img/1/3479.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(492, 'Alone', 4, '<p>As one group finds what may be an ideal shelter, another group comes to realize that the best protection comes from those around them.</p>', 13, 4, 60, '2014-03-09', '/img/1/3480.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(493, 'The Grove', 4, '<p>After finding an idyllic place to establish a new shelter, the group starts to question whether it is possible to go back to the way things were.</p>', 14, 4, 60, '2014-03-16', '/img/1/3481.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(494, 'Us', 4, '<p>However brutal some survivors believe they must be to stay alive, we get to see that faith can sometimes be the strongest survival tool.</p>', 15, 4, 60, '2014-03-23', '/img/1/3482.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(495, 'A', 4, '<p>As multiple paths collide, Rick comes face to face with sheer brutality. Will he and the group have what it takes to survive?</p>', 16, 4, 60, '2014-03-30', '/img/1/3483.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(496, 'No Sanctuary', 4, '<p>The true motives of the Terminans come to light when Rick and the others end up in a vulnerable situation.</p>', 1, 5, 60, '2014-10-12', '/img/1/4576.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(497, 'Strangers', 4, '<p>With supplies running low and not knowing whether to trust the people around them, Rick leads a mission where the risk might not be worth the reward.</p>', 2, 5, 60, '2014-10-19', '/img/1/4761.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(498, 'Four Walls and a Roof', 4, '<p>Rick and the group find themselves pitted against some very nasty people, but they might just have a plan to gain the upper hand.</p>', 3, 5, 60, '2014-10-26', '/img/2/5456.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(499, 'Slabtown', 4, '<p>In this episode, we get to meet a whole group of other survivors, but what looks safe and nice on the outside has a bit of a dark side.</p>', 4, 5, 60, '2014-11-02', '/img/2/6600.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(500, 'Self Help', 4, '<p>A new set of issues confront our group while on a mission. Will they be able to push through and survive these challenges? Or better yet, each other?</p>', 5, 5, 60, '2014-11-09', '/img/3/9711.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(501, 'Consumed', 4, '<p>Cautiously, members of our group must venture into a familiar location on a heroic rescue mission. It\'s a huge stage, but so are the stakes.</p>', 6, 5, 60, '2014-11-16', '/img/4/11017.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(502, 'Crossed', 4, '<p>Between holding down the church and going on a rescue mission, our group is spread pretty thin. Is this going to be the breaking point?</p>', 7, 5, 60, '2014-11-23', '/img/4/12437.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(503, 'Coda', 4, '<p>Rick seeks a peaceful agreement when rules and morals are tossed aside by new enemies.</p>', 8, 5, 60, '2014-11-30', '/img/5/13527.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(504, 'What Happened and What\'s Going On', 4, '<p>After the recent trials the group has faced, a slight detour could be the solution they\'ve been searching for.</p>', 9, 5, 60, '2015-02-08', '/img/8/21352.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(505, 'Them', 4, '<p>Life on the road has left the group beaten and beleaguered. Will they be able to trudge along? Are they even the same people they once were?</p>', 10, 5, 60, '2015-02-15', '/img/8/21711.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(506, 'The Distance', 4, '<p>After a spectacular storm, Rick and the group meet a seemingly friendly person.</p>', 11, 5, 60, '2015-02-22', '/img/8/22179.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(507, 'Remember', 4, '<p>Molding into a new lifestyle is proving difficult for the group. Has life on the road proven too treacherous to go back to who they once were?</p>', 12, 5, 60, '2015-03-01', '/img/9/22728.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(508, 'Forget', 4, '<p>Rick and the group continue to acclimate to their new surroundings. Will they be able to go back to normalcy? Better yet, what is normal now?</p>', 13, 5, 60, '2015-03-08', '/img/9/22756.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(509, 'Spend', 4, '<p>While trying to secure their new home, Rick and his group face many challenges, some life threatening. Is this really the utopia it seems to be?</p>', 14, 5, 60, '2015-03-15', '/img/9/23227.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(510, 'Try', 4, '<p>The group realizes that sheltered life might not be possible as life within the walls starts to mimic life outside. Will these setbacks break Rick?</p>', 15, 5, 60, '2015-03-22', '/img/9/23993.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(511, 'Conquer', 4, '<p>Daryl experiences trouble on a run while Rick and his group continue to feel like outsiders in Alexandria, where trouble is creeping into the gates.</p>', 16, 5, 60, '2015-03-29', '/img/9/24246.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(512, 'First Time Again', 4, '<p>Rick and the others have a difficult time assimilating into Alexandria; a new threat arises that could bring the group closer together.</p>', 1, 6, 90, '2015-10-11', '/img/25/64934.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(513, 'JSS', 4, '<p>When it appears that things are starting to normalize in the settlement, a new problem arises for the Alexandrians.</p>', 2, 6, 60, '2015-10-18', '/img/25/64935.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(514, 'Thank You', 4, '<p>Rick and his group get caught up in a dangerous little town on the road back to Alexandria. Meanwhile, Daryl, Sasha and Abraham continue to lead away the remaining walkers away from the safe-zone.</p>', 3, 6, 60, '2015-10-25', '/img/26/65943.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(515, 'Here\'s Not Here', 4, '<p>A new face appears; trust issues form.</p>', 4, 6, 90, '2015-11-01', '/img/28/70292.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(516, 'Now', 4, '<p>Following a number of setbacks, the mood in Alexandria grows grim for the sheltered citizens.</p>', 5, 6, 60, '2015-11-08', '/img/30/75163.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(517, 'Always Accountable', 4, '<p>Daryl, Abraham and Sasha encounter many obstacles and a new threat while trying to return to Alexandria.</p>', 6, 6, 60, '2015-11-15', '/img/31/78072.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(518, 'Heads Up', 4, '<p>Alexandria is finally able to begin pulling itself back together; peace is embraced between the two groups.</p>', 7, 6, 60, '2015-11-22', '/img/32/81183.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(519, 'Start to Finish', 4, '<p>After having a few moments of peace, trouble finds its way to Alexandria yet again. Only this time, the threat might be too big to defeat.</p>', 8, 6, 60, '2015-11-29', '/img/32/82293.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(520, 'No Way Out', 4, '<p>With walkers inside the gates of Alexandria, Rick and the group are scared, outnumbered and things are only getting worse.</p>', 9, 6, 60, '2016-02-14', '/img/45/112611.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(521, 'The Next World', 4, '<p>A simple scavenging run proves to be more tricky, when the survivors are not the only ones after a goldmine of supplies.</p>', 10, 6, 60, '2016-02-21', '/img/46/115053.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(522, 'Knots Untie', 4, '<p>After Rick comes to the realization that Alexandria might not be as safe as he thought, decisions must be made about where to go from here.</p><p><i><br></i></p>', 11, 6, 60, '2016-02-28', '/img/47/117541.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(523, 'Not Tomorrow Yet', 4, '<p>Rick and the group realize the only way to maintain the peace of Alexandria is to fight a new enemy. This time, though, our group might be outmatched.</p>', 12, 6, 60, '2016-03-06', '/img/48/120370.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(524, 'The Same Boat', 4, '<p>With no hope of safety in Alexandria, Rick and his band of survivors soon discover a larger world with new dangers and new opportunities.</p>', 13, 6, 60, '2016-03-13', '/img/49/122738.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(525, 'Twice as Far', 4, '<p>Two separate groups leave Alexandria for supplies, and while both worry over the future of the community, they will face immediate danger.</p>', 14, 6, 60, '2016-03-20', '/img/49/124618.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(526, 'East', 4, '<p>When someone goes missing in Alexandria, the community goes on alert, and search parties venture out.</p>', 15, 6, 60, '2016-03-27', '/img/51/127564.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(527, 'Last Day on Earth', 4, '<p>In the aftermath of a tragic blow, Eugene falls captured by Dwight, a member of the Saviors, whom are hell bent on getting even with Alexandria, Negan teaches Rick and co a brutal lesson, which shows that Rick and co finally have something to fear.</p>', 16, 6, 90, '2016-04-03', '/img/51/129668.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(528, 'The Day Will Come When You Won\'t Be', 4, '<p>Last season ended with Rick and our group kneeling helplessly before Negan and his group; what Negan does will haunt those who survive forever.</p>', 1, 7, 60, '2016-10-23', '/img/81/204734.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(529, 'The Well', 4, '<p>For a number of familiar faces, a new, well-established community seems too good to be true.</p>', 2, 7, 60, '2016-10-30', '/img/84/210152.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(530, 'The Cell', 4, '<p>A new group of survivors seem to have it all in their impressive community; however, there is a price.</p>', 3, 7, 60, '2016-11-06', '/img/84/210151.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(531, 'Service', 4, '<p>The remaining members of the group try to keep it together in Alexandria; they receive a sobering visit.</p>', 4, 7, 85, '2016-11-13', '/img/84/211847.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(532, 'Go Getters', 4, '<p>Saddled with grief and surrounded by enemies, members of the group try to find safety at the Hilltop before it\'s too late.</p>', 5, 7, 60, '2016-11-20', '/img/84/211848.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(533, 'Swear', 4, '<p>Someone stumbles upon a brand new society, and this society is unlike anything seen before.</p>', 6, 7, 60, '2016-11-27', '/img/86/217448.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(534, 'Sing Me a Song', 4, '<p>A deeper look at the Sanctuary and the world of the Saviors; members of Alexandria look for supplies.</p>', 7, 7, 60, '2016-12-04', '/img/87/219924.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(535, 'Hearts Still Beating', 4, '<p>Negan\'s unwelcome visit to Alexandria continues as other members scavenge for supplies; things quickly spin out of control.</p>', 8, 7, 60, '2016-12-11', '/img/88/222262.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(536, 'Rock in the Road', 4, '<p>Rick is introduced to a new community.</p>', 9, 7, 73, '2017-02-12', '/img/98/245711.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(537, 'New Best Friends', 4, '<p>While searching for a missing Alexandrian, Rick and his group encounter a mysterious collective, its inhabitants unlike any they have come across.</p>', 10, 7, 60, '2017-02-19', '/img/99/249101.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(538, 'Hostiles and Calamities', 4, '<p>An Alexandrian discovers they must navigate the mysterious, confusing and terrifying world within the Saviors\' compound.</p>', 11, 7, 60, '2017-02-26', '/img/100/250430.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(539, 'Say Yes', 4, '<p>The group scavenges for supplies; back in Alexandria, someone must make a morally challenging decision.</p>', 12, 7, 60, '2017-03-05', '/img/101/253221.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(540, 'Bury Me Here', 4, '<p>Things do not go as planned when a group of Kingdommers delivers goods to the Saviors during a routine supply drop-off.</p>', 13, 7, 60, '2017-03-12', '/img/102/255064.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(541, 'The Other Side', 4, '<p>The Saviors visit the Hilltop unexpectedly, surprising everyone, with plans of taking more than supplies.</p>', 14, 7, 60, '2017-03-19', '/img/102/257406.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(542, 'Something They Need', 4, '<p>A group of Alexandrians embarks on a journey; one member of the group must make a heartbreaking decision.</p>', 15, 7, 60, '2017-03-26', '/img/103/258072.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(543, 'The First Day of the Rest of Your Life', 4, '<p>The stakes continue to grow higher as paths cross; the group enacts an intricate plan.</p>', 16, 7, 60, '2017-04-02', '/img/104/260887.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(544, 'Mercy', 4, '<p>Rick and his group, along with the Kingdom and Hilltop, have banded together to bring the fight to Negan and the Saviors.</p>', 1, 8, 60, '2017-10-22', '/img/132/330943.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(545, 'The Damned', 4, '<p>The plan involving Alexandrians, Kingdommers and Hilltoppers unfolds; as Rick continues to fight, he encounters a familiar face.</p>', 2, 8, 60, '2017-10-29', '/img/133/332920.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(546, 'Monsters', 4, '<p>Conflict with the Saviors leads to unintended consequences for the Hilltop, the Kingdom, and Alexandria; morality proves tricky in wartime.</p>', 3, 8, 60, '2017-11-05', '/img/134/335146.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(547, 'Some Guy', 4, '<p>A new weapon in the Savior arsenal proves to be a giant hurdle as fighting continues between Rick\'s forces and those of the Saviors.</p>', 4, 8, 60, '2017-11-12', '/img/134/337406.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(548, 'The Big Scary U', 4, '<p>A close look at Negan and the lives of the Saviors during the conflict through a familiar set of eyes.</p>', 5, 8, 60, '2017-11-19', '/img/135/339450.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(549, 'The King, the Widow, and Rick', 4, '<p>With things looking up for Rick and the group, an argument breaks out at the Hilltop; the consequences of the decision are life versus death.</p>', 6, 8, 60, '2017-11-26', '/img/136/341547.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(550, 'Time for After', 4, '<p>Negan has to enlist the help of his lieutenants in solving a huge issue facing the Sanctuary; Rick and the group continue to enact the plan.</p>', 7, 8, 60, '2017-12-03', '/img/137/343481.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(551, 'How It\'s Gotta Be', 4, '<p>Every story and battle from the first half of the season comes crashing together in this action-packed, emotional mid-season finale.</p>', 8, 8, 88, '2017-12-10', '/img/138/345620.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(552, 'Honor', 4, '<p>Rick faces new difficulties after a battle. Meanwhile, the fight continues in other communities as core members face hard decisions.</p>', 9, 8, 60, '2018-02-25', '/img/147/367863.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(553, 'The Lost and the Plunderers', 4, '<p>Groups unite their forces and converge on the Hilltop; Aaron and Enid search for allies.</p>', 10, 8, 60, '2018-03-04', '/img/147/369793.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(554, 'Dead or Alive Or', 4, '<p>Daryl finds himself in bad company as his group heads to the Hilltop; Gabriel\'s faith gets tested.</p>', 11, 8, 60, '2018-03-11', '/img/148/371989.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(555, 'The Key', 4, '<p>Hilltop\'s leadership faces a difficult dilemma after the arrival of unexpected visitors; Rick comes face to face with an adversary.</p>', 12, 8, 60, '2018-03-18', '/img/148/371804.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
(556, 'Do Not Send Us Astray', 4, '<p>Trouble arises when unexpected visitors arrive at the Hilltop and the community is thrust into action; heartbreaking discoveries are made.</p>', 13, 8, 60, '2018-03-25', '/img/150/376680.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
