(558, 'Worth', 4, '<p>With the threat of the Saviors still looming, Aaron continues searching for allies; Daryl and Rosita take action and confront an old friend.</p>', 15, 8, 60, '2018-04-08', '/img/152/380620.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:01', '2019-12-19 02:15:01'),
