(1970, 'The Blue Comet', 18, '<p>The Beginning of the End. Phil finally puts the hits on the Soprano clan and Tony puts a hit on Phil which results in mistaken identity making everyone think its safe when its not and it results in a Death and Coma. After this happens Tony separates from his family to go into hiding as he sends Carmela, Janice, and the kids into hiding.</p>', 20, 6, 60, '2007-06-03', '/img/201/504373.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
