(2140, 'The Smugglers, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor discovers Polly and Ben aboard the TARDIS shortly before the ship arrives in 17th century Cornwall, where the local churchwarden gives the Doctor a cryptic message shortly before being murdered.</p>', 1, 4, 25, '1966-09-10', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2141, 'The Smugglers, Part Two', 20, '<p>Pike is convinced that the Doctor knows the location of Avery\'s treasure while Polly and Ben try to convince the locals they were not responsible for Longfoot\'s murder.</p>', 2, 4, 25, '1966-09-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2142, 'The Smugglers, Part Three', 20, '<p>Polly and Ben are placed in the custody of Blake, who reveals he also has his suspicions about the Squire, while the Doctor and Kewper are forced to team up to escape from Pike\'s ship.</p>', 3, 4, 25, '1966-09-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2143, 'The Smugglers, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends are at the mercy of Cherub, who is now seeking Avery\'s treasure for himself, while Pike prepares to attack the village.</p>', 4, 4, 25, '1966-10-01', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2144, 'The Tenth Planet, Part One', 20, '<p>In December 1986, a new planet appears in the Solar System which turns out to be a long-lost twin of Earth\'s named Mondas. Its inhabitants are the Cybermen.</p>', 5, 4, 25, '1966-10-08', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2145, 'The Tenth Planet, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor\'s warnings are ignored and the Cybermen take over the base, hampering the crew\'s efforts to help Zeus IV.</p>', 6, 4, 25, '1966-10-15', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2146, 'The Tenth Planet, Part Three', 20, '<p>With the Doctor out of action, it is up to Polly, Ben and Barclay to stop Cutler using the Z-Bomb and devastating half the world.</p>', 7, 4, 25, '1966-10-22', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2147, 'The Tenth Planet, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Cybermen take over the base again, apparently to stop the humans using the Z-Bomb, but then the Doctor realises they intend to use it themselves to destroy Earth.</p>', 8, 4, 25, '1966-10-29', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2148, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his companions are brought to an Earth colony on the planet Vulcan.</p>', 9, 4, 25, '1966-11-05', '/img/90/225956.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2149, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor warns the scientist about the dire consequences of reactivating the dormant Dalek that he claims not to have discovered. The Doctor attempts to see the governor in an attempt to stop the secret experiments with the Dalek,.</p>', 10, 4, 25, '1966-11-12', '/img/90/225962.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2150, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>Polly is taken prisoner by the rebels who are planning to use the Dalek to take control of the colony.</p>', 11, 4, 25, '1966-11-19', '/img/90/225969.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2151, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>Scientist Lesterson discovers the Daleks plot to reproduce themselves and then seize control of the Colony.</p>', 12, 4, 25, '1966-11-26', '/img/90/225970.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2152, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part Five', 20, '<p>The head of security for the Earth colony Vulcan, leads a rebellion; The Daleks prepare to make their final assault on the people of the colony.</p>', 13, 4, 25, '1966-12-03', '/img/91/228083.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2153, 'The Power of the Daleks, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Daleks begin their attack while the battle rages between the loyalists and the rebels and it falls to the Doctor to make an attempt to stop the Daleks plot.</p>', 14, 4, 25, '1966-12-10', '/img/91/228431.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2154, 'The Highlanders, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Polly and Ben arrive in 1746, in the aftermath of the Battle of Culloden, and are captured by a group of Highlanders shortly before they themselves are captured by redcoats.</p>', 15, 4, 25, '1966-12-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2155, 'The Highlanders, Part Two', 20, '<p>Polly and Kirsty capture Lieutenant Ffinch to try and enlist his help while the Doctor tricks Gray in order to escape.</p>', 16, 4, 25, '1966-12-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2156, 'The Highlanders, Part Three', 20, '<p>With the Highlanders imprisoned aboard Trask\'s ship, the Doctor attempts to expose Grey\'s plan.</p>', 17, 4, 25, '1966-12-31', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2157, 'The Highlanders, Part Four', 20, '<p>Ben manages to join up with the Doctor, Polly and Kirsty and together they work to free the Highlanders from Trask\'s ship before Grey sells them into slavery.</p>', 18, 4, 25, '1967-01-07', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2158, 'The Underwater Menace, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS materializes on a stretch of deserted beach. The Doctor and his companions are then captured and taken to the mysterious lost city of Atlantis.</p>', 19, 4, 25, '1967-01-14', '/img/58/145505.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2159, 'The Underwater Menace, Part Two', 20, '<p>While Ara tries to save Polly from being turned into a Fish Person and Ben and Jamie try to escape from the mines, the Doctor discovers the full extent of Zaroff\'s plans.</p>', 20, 4, 25, '1967-01-21', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2160, 'The Underwater Menace, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Ramo are sentenced to be sacrificed to the goddess Amdo and must escape to put a stop to Zaroff\'s plan.</p>', 21, 4, 25, '1967-01-28', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2161, 'The Underwater Menace, Part Four', 20, '<p>With Zaroff\'s plan nearing completion, the Doctor and Ben realise the only way to save the world is to destroy Atlantis.</p>', 22, 4, 25, '1967-02-04', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2162, 'The Moonbase, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS arrives on the Moon in the year 2070. When Jamie is injured, the other travellers are forced to seek the help of a moonbase afflicted with a space plague.</p>', 23, 4, 25, '1967-02-11', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2163, 'The Moonbase, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends attempt to convince the Moonbase crew that the Cybermen are responsible for the disappearances and find a cure for the plague.</p>', 24, 4, 25, '1967-02-18', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2164, 'The Moonbase, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Cybermen take over the Moonbase and begin using the Gravitron to attack Earth but Polly, Ben and Jamie come up with a way to fight back.</p>', 25, 4, 25, '1967-02-25', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2165, 'The Moonbase, Part Four', 20, '<p>With the Cybermen preparing to launch a full attack, the Doctor and his friends must keep the Moonbase and the Gravitron out of their hands until help arrives from Earth.</p>', 26, 4, 25, '1967-03-04', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2166, 'The Macra Terror, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS arrives at a holiday camp company with the crew worried by a prediction of giant crabs and the Doctor becomes interested in the apparent madman Medok\'s stories of creatures that roam the colony at night.</p>', 27, 4, 25, '1967-03-11', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2167, 'The Macra Terror, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is unable to convince the colonists that the Macra exist and an attempt to brainwash his companions results in Ben betraying his friends.</p>', 28, 4, 25, '1967-03-18', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2168, 'The Macra Terror, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Polly and Jamie are sentenced to work in the pits and an escape attempt sees Ben\'s loyalties called into question again.</p>', 29, 4, 25, '1967-03-25', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2169, 'The Macra Terror, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Polly manage to save Jamie from the Macra and then try to show the Pilot who is really in charge of the colony.</p>', 30, 4, 25, '1967-04-01', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2170, 'The Faceless Ones, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS materialises on the runway of Gatwick Airport, where Polly witnesses a murder only to be kidnapped before she can report it.</p>', 31, 4, 25, '1967-04-08', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2171, 'The Faceless Ones, Part Two', 20, '<p>With Polly having apparently forgotten them, the Doctor, Ben and Jamie decide to carry out their own investigation of Chameleon Tours.</p>', 32, 4, 25, '1967-04-15', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2172, 'The Faceless Ones, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Sam manage to convince Crossland to trust them and he persuades the Commandant to let them continue their investigation.</p>', 33, 4, 25, '1967-04-22', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2173, 'The Faceless Ones, Part Four', 20, '<p>When Spencer attempts to kill them, the Doctor, Jamie and Sam become convinced Chameleon Tours are hiding something and Sam decides to book a ticket on one of their flights.</p>', 34, 4, 25, '1967-04-29', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2174, 'The Faceless Ones, Part Five', 20, '<p>Jamie finds himself aboard the Chameleons\' satellite and meets their Director while the Doctor forces the Chameleon Meadows to tell him the aliens\' plans.</p>', 35, 4, 25, '1967-05-06', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:07', '2019-12-19 02:15:07'),
(2175, 'The Faceless Ones, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Pinto are captured by the Chameleons but the Doctor manages to use their dependence on their human originals to create dissent in their ranks.</p>', 36, 4, 25, '1967-05-13', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2176, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>Trying to find the stolen TARDIS, the Doctor and Jamie are lured into a trap by the Doctor\'s old enemies the Daleks.</p>', 37, 4, 25, '1967-05-20', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2177, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie investigate Waterfield\'s antiques shop, where they are knocked unconscious and transported back to the 19th century.</p>', 38, 4, 25, '1967-05-27', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2178, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>As part of the Daleks\' experiment, the Doctor manipulates Jamie into attempting to rescue Victoria.</p>', 39, 4, 25, '1967-06-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2179, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>Jamie and Kemel team up to try and find Victoria, while the Doctor and the Daleks continue to monitor their progress.</p>', 40, 4, 25, '1967-06-10', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2180, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Five', 20, '<p>With the experiment at an end, the Doctor begins to suspect the key to rescuing Jamie, Victoria and Kemel from the Daleks lies with Terrall.</p>', 41, 4, 25, '1967-06-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2181, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Waterfield follow the Daleks to Skaro, where they discover an unforeseen consequence to their experiment.</p>', 42, 4, 25, '1967-06-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2182, 'The Evil of the Daleks, Part Seven', 20, '<p>The Daleks are poised to spread the Dalek Factor throughout the history of Earth and begin by implanting the Doctor.</p>', 43, 4, 25, '1967-07-01', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2183, 'The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria arrive on Telos, where an archaeological group are exploring the Tomb of the Cybermen. But are the Cybermen as dormant as they believe?</p>', 1, 5, 25, '1967-09-02', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2184, 'The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Two', 20, '<p>The archaeologists learn they are stranded on Telos and Klieg suggests they use the opportunity to explore the Cybermen\'s tombs.</p>', 2, 5, 25, '1967-09-09', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2185, 'The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Cybermen have been revived and plan to convert the archeologists into their own kind, prompting Hopper to attempt a rescue.</p>', 3, 5, 25, '1967-09-16', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2186, 'The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Four', 20, '<p>Klieg attempts to do a deal with the Cybercontroller while the Doctor tries to find a way to refreeze the Cybermen permanently.</p>', 4, 5, 25, '1967-09-23', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2187, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part One', 20, '<p>When the TARDIS materialises in the Himalayas, the Doctor decides to pay a return visit to the nearby Det-Sen monastery only to be accused of murder.</p>', 5, 5, 25, '1967-09-30', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2188, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part Two', 20, '<p>Jamie and Victoria make their way to the monastery shortly before it is attacked by the Yeti.</p>', 6, 5, 25, '1967-10-07', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2189, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part Three', 20, '<p>While the Doctor and Jamie return to the TARDIS for equipment, the control sphere Jamie brought to the monastery is reactivated.</p>', 7, 5, 25, '1967-10-14', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2190, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Yeti escapes from the monastery and Victoria and Thonmi are accused of assisting it, while the Doctor and Jamie endure a perilous journey back across the mountains.</p>', 8, 5, 25, '1967-10-21', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2191, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part Five', 20, '<p>Victoria falls under the mental influence of Padmasambhva as the Yeti attack in order to drive the monks from the area.</p>', 9, 5, 25, '1967-10-28', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2192, 'The Abominable Snowmen, Part Six', 20, '<p>With the Great Intelligence on the verge of becoming corporeal, the Doctor challenges Padmasambhva to a mental battle in order to defeat it.</p>', 10, 5, 25, '1967-11-04', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2193, 'The Ice Warriors, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria are brought to a base which is attempting to halt the flow of the Second Ice Age.</p>', 11, 5, 25, '1967-11-11', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2194, 'The Ice Warriors, Part Two', 20, '<p>Varga revives and takes Victoria hostage as he works to revive his crew while the Doctor and Jamie find Penley stealing medical supplies.</p>', 12, 5, 25, '1967-11-18', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2195, 'The Ice Warriors, Part Three', 20, '<p>Jamie and Arden venture out to rescue Victoria only to find the rest of the Ice Warriors are now active.</p>', 13, 5, 25, '1967-11-25', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2196, 'The Ice Warriors, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor leaves the base to try and find Jamie and Victoria while Storr tries to do a deal with the Ice Warriors.</p>', 14, 5, 25, '1967-12-02', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2197, 'The Ice Warriors, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Victoria are both held prisoner by the Ice Warriors as Varga decides to take over Brittanicus.</p>', 15, 5, 25, '1967-12-09', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2198, 'The Ice Warriors, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Victoria attempt to force the Ice Warriors to surrender control of the ioniser before the ice flow destroys them.</p>', 16, 5, 25, '1967-12-16', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2199, 'The Enemy of the World, Part One', 20, '<p>After the Doctor is attacked by a group of mysterious gunmen, he discovers he is the physical double of the famous scientist Salamander.</p>', 17, 5, 25, '1967-12-23', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2200, 'The Enemy of the World, Part Two', 20, '<p>Jamie and Victoria agree to accompany Astrid to Hungary to observe Salamander\'s activities.</p>', 18, 5, 25, '1967-12-30', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2201, 'The Enemy of the World, Part Three', 20, '<p>Jamie and Victoria become friends with Fariah, determined to discover the truth about Salamander. Astrid makes plans to rescue Denes, but not everything goes to plan.</p>', 19, 5, 25, '1968-01-06', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2202, 'The Enemy of the World, Part Four', 20, '<p>Fariah brings the Doctor and Kent evidence of Salamander\'s activities but then they come under attack from Benik.</p>', 20, 5, 25, '1968-01-13', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2203, 'The Enemy of the World, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor persuades Bruce to help him infiltrate Salamander\'s research centre while Salamander takes drastic action to prevent Swann finding out the truth.</p>', 21, 5, 25, '1968-01-20', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2204, 'The Enemy of the World, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor discovers the true link between Salamander and Kent while Astrid tries to convince the shelter inhabitants they have been lied to.</p>', 22, 5, 25, '1968-01-27', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2205, 'The Web of Fear, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS becomes trapped in space before ending up in an underground station of a mysteriously deserted London.</p>', 23, 5, 25, '1968-02-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2206, 'The Web of Fear, Part Two', 20, '<p>Jamie and Victoria are reunited with Travers before Jamie joins the soldiers in attempting to find out what has happened to the Doctor.</p>', 24, 5, 25, '1968-02-10', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2207, 'The Web of Fear, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Victoria are taken back to the Goodge Street base by Colonel Lethbridge-Stewart where the Doctor becomes convinced there is a traitor in their midst.</p>', 25, 5, 25, '1968-02-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2208, 'The Web of Fear, Part Four', 20, '<p>With Travers having been captured by the Yeti, the Doctor attempts to find a way to gain control of the robots while Lethbridge-Stewart tries to recover the TARDIS.</p>', 26, 5, 25, '1968-02-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2209, 'The Web of Fear, Part Five', 20, '<p>Victoria and Travers are held prisoner by the Great Intelligence, who is planning to drain the Doctor\'s mind.</p>', 27, 5, 25, '1968-03-02', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2210, 'The Web of Fear, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends are held prisoner by the Intelligence and their only hope lies with Jamie, Arnold and a reprogrammed Yeti.</p>', 28, 5, 25, '1968-03-09', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2211, 'Fury from the Deep, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria are taken prisoner by the staff of a gas refinery, who have lost contact with their drilling rigs and experienced mysterious drops in pressure.</p>', 29, 5, 25, '1968-03-16', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2212, 'Fury from the Deep, Part Two', 20, '<p>Harris asks for the Doctor\'s help with Maggie with Van Lutyens and the Chief Engineer attempt to find out what is blocking the impeller.</p>', 30, 5, 25, '1968-03-23', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2213, 'Fury from the Deep, Part Three', 20, '<p>While the Doctor begins his investigation into the weed creatures, Robson is attacked by one at the refinery.</p>', 31, 5, 25, '1968-03-30', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2214, 'Fury from the Deep, Part Four', 20, '<p>Van Lutyens\' investigation of the base of the impeller places the Doctor and Jamie in danger from the Weed Creature.</p>', 32, 5, 25, '1968-04-06', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2215, 'Fury from the Deep, Part Five', 20, '<p>With the Weed Creature poised to burst out of the pipeline and attack the base, an encounter with Oak and Quill gives the Doctor a vital clue about its weakness.</p>', 33, 5, 25, '1968-04-13', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2216, 'Fury from the Deep, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie rescue Victoria from Robson and realise they can destroy the Weed Creature with sound waves.</p>', 34, 5, 25, '1968-04-20', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2217, 'The Wheel in Space, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie arrive on a mysterious spacecraft whose only occupant is a dangerous Servo Robot.</p>', 35, 5, 25, '1968-04-27', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2218, 'The Wheel in Space, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie are brought aboard the Wheel where Jamie is horrified to learn the crew plan to destroy the Silver Carrier with the TARDIS on board.</p>', 36, 5, 25, '1968-05-04', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2219, 'The Wheel in Space, Part Three', 20, '<p>Jamie sabotages the Wheel\'s x-ray laser, unknowingly giving the Cybermen an opportunity to reach the Wheel.</p>', 37, 5, 25, '1968-05-11', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2220, 'The Wheel in Space, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Cybermen instruct their human slaves to smuggle them onto the Wheel while the Doctor attempts to convince Bennett of the threat they pose.</p>', 38, 5, 25, '1968-05-18', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2221, 'The Wheel in Space, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Cybermen gain control of more members of the Wheel crew and the Doctor realises the only way to stop them is for Jamie and Zoe to make a dangerous space walk.</p>', 39, 5, 25, '1968-05-25', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2222, 'The Wheel in Space, Part Six', 20, '<p>Jamie and Zoe attempt to recover the time vector generator while the Cybermen realise the Doctor is on the Wheel and make him their prime target.</p>', 40, 5, 25, '1968-06-01', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2223, 'The Dominators, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS arrives on the planet Dulkis where the Doctor, Zoe and Jamie decide to have a quiet holiday. Only to find the Evil Dominators and their robotic slaves, The Quarks have arrived on a radioactive island, where they plan to detonate a bomb in the planet\'s core, which will turn the entire planet as source of radioactive fuel for their invasion fleet.</p>', 1, 6, 25, '1968-08-10', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2224, 'The Dominators, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie are captured by the Dominators, who subject them to an intelligence test, while Zoe and Cully attempt to convince the Dulcian council of the threat.</p>', 2, 6, 25, '1968-08-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2225, 'The Dominators, Part Three', 20, '<p>Zoe and Cully are captured by the Dominators and put to work alongside the survey team while the Doctor and Jamie decide to return to the island to help.</p>', 3, 6, 25, '1968-08-24', '/img/112/281604.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2226, 'The Dominators, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Zoe are interrogated by Rago, who is planning to present his terms to the Dulcian council, while Jamie and Cully try to find a way to strike back against the Quarks.</p>', 4, 6, 25, '1968-08-31', '/img/112/281605.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2227, 'The Dominators, Part Five', 20, '<p>Jamie and Cully manage to rescue the Doctor\'s party and together they try to find a way to stop the Dominators before they destroy the entire planet.</p>', 5, 6, 25, '1968-09-07', '/img/112/281609.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2228, 'The Mind Robber, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor activates an emergency unit on board theTARDIS to escape destruction by a volcanic eruption. Unfortunately, it moves them out of normal space and time to a deadly world where fantasy rules. The travellers find themselves lured out of the ship into a ghostly white void.</p>', 6, 6, 25, '1968-09-14', '/img/112/281610.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2229, 'The Mind Robber, Part Two', 20, '<p>With the TARDIS destroyed, the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe find themselves in a strange forest patrolled by mysterious soldiers.</p>', 7, 6, 25, '1968-09-21', '/img/112/281611.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2230, 'The Mind Robber, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor realises that the travelers are trapped in a world where fiction is real and where creatures are a threat if people believe in them.</p>', 8, 6, 25, '1968-09-28', '/img/112/281612.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2231, 'The Mind Robber, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe reach the citadel at the centre of the land, where they finally encounter the Master of the Land of Fiction.</p>', 9, 6, 25, '1968-10-05', '/img/112/281613.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2232, 'The Mind Robber, Part Five', 20, '<p>With Jamie and Zoe having been turned into fiction, the Doctor must find a way to save them without suffering the same fate or becoming part of the Master Brain.</p>', 10, 6, 25, '1968-10-12', '/img/112/281615.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2233, 'The Invasion, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS lands in London where the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe agree to help find Isobel Watkins\' missing uncle.Searching for Professor Watkins at his last place of work,a multinational electronics supplier, hemeets the company\'s managing director. He\'s not what he seems - and possesses alien technology in his office.</p>', 11, 6, 25, '1968-11-02', '/img/112/281623.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2234, 'The Invasion, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie are taken prisoner by their mysterious observers and have a reunion with an old friend while Zoe and Isobel carry out their own investigation of IE.</p>', 12, 6, 25, '1968-11-09', '/img/112/281627.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2235, 'The Invasion, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie return to the IE factory in search of Zoe and Isobel, where they meet with Professor Watkins and fall foul of Vaughn.</p>', 13, 6, 25, '1968-11-16', '/img/112/281629.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2236, 'The Invasion, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie enlist the help of UNIT to rescue Zoe and Isobel before trying to find out what Vaughn is really up to.</p>', 14, 6, 25, '1968-11-23', '/img/112/281649.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2237, 'The Invasion, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jamie tell the Brigadier about the Cybermen but with Rutledge under Vaughn\'s control he is powerless to act.</p>', 15, 6, 25, '1968-11-30', '/img/112/281784.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2238, 'The Invasion, Part Six', 20, '<p>Captain Turner manages to rescue Jamie and the others, while the Doctor begins working on a way to protect everyone from the Cybermen\'s hypno-sound signal.</p>', 16, 6, 25, '1968-12-07', '/img/112/281794.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2239, 'The Invasion, Part Seven', 20, '<p>With the entire world unconscious apart from the Doctor and his friends, the Cybermen are poised to invade and only Zoe, the Brigadier and a missile crew can stop them.</p>', 17, 6, 25, '1968-12-14', '/img/112/281796.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2240, 'The Invasion, Part Eight', 20, '<p>The Cybermen have launched their deadly megatron bomb which will destroy all life on Earth unless the Doctor can deactivate the homing signal.</p>', 18, 6, 25, '1968-12-21', '/img/112/281812.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2241, 'The Krotons, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS lands on the planet of the Gonds, a primitive and enslaved people. Every year, two of the finest Gond students are sent to be \'companions\' of the mysterious and unseen Krotons. But the Doctor reveals that only death awaits them.</p>', 19, 6, 25, '1968-12-28', '/img/112/281813.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2242, 'The Krotons, Part Two', 20, '<p>Zoe is selected as a companion for the Krotons and the Doctor insists on joining her.</p>', 20, 6, 25, '1969-01-04', '/img/112/281814.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2243, 'The Krotons, Part Three', 20, '<p>Jamie is held prisoner by the Krotons who intend to recapture the Doctor and Zoe for their mental energy.</p>', 21, 6, 25, '1969-01-11', '/img/112/281816.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2244, 'The Krotons, Part Four', 20, '<p>Selris succeeds in drawing the Krotons out of the Dynatrope but Eelek agrees to hand the Doctor and Zoe over to them in return for their leaving the planet.</p>', 22, 6, 25, '1969-01-18', '/img/112/281828.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2245, 'The Seeds of Death, Part One', 20, '<p>21st century Earth is entirely dependent on the T-Mat transport system but the control centre on the moon has stopped functioning. Meanwhile, the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe meet the one man who can solve the crisis.</p>', 23, 6, 25, '1969-01-25', '/img/112/281829.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2246, 'The Seeds of Death, Part Two', 20, '<p>Eldred agrees to supply a rocket for travel to the moon and the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe volunteer to crew it.</p>', 24, 6, 25, '1969-02-01', '/img/112/281830.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2247, 'The Seeds of Death, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe make it to the moon and join forces with Phipps but the Ice Warriors have gained control of T-mat.</p>', 25, 6, 25, '1969-02-08', '/img/112/281831.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2248, 'The Seeds of Death, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Ice Warriors\' seed pods beginning materialising all over the globe while Slaar decides to kill the Doctor by T-matting him into space.</p>', 26, 6, 25, '1969-02-15', '/img/112/281832.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2249, 'The Seeds of Death, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his allies manage to return to Earth via T-mat only to find the Ice Warrior has attacked the weather control station.</p>', 27, 6, 25, '1969-02-22', '/img/112/281929.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2250, 'The Seeds of Death, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor manages to create a rain storm to destroy the Martian fungus before trying to find a way to stop the Ice Warriors\' invasion fleet.</p>', 28, 6, 25, '1969-03-01', '/img/112/281935.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2251, 'The Space Pirates, Part One', 20, '<p>Space beacons are being destroyed by pirates, who are salvaging the argonite metal. When the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe arrive on one of the beacons, they are mistaken for pirates.</p>', 29, 6, 25, '1969-03-08', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2252, 'The Space Pirates, Part Two', 20, '<p>With the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe trapped on a beacon segment, Hermack becomes suspicious of the unruly prospector Milo Clancey.</p>', 30, 6, 25, '1969-03-15', '/img/112/281936.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2253, 'The Space Pirates, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe flee from the Space Corps with Clancey, who decides to seek refuge on Ta.</p>', 31, 6, 25, '1969-03-22', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2254, 'The Space Pirates, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe are held prisoner by the space pirates while Caven comes up with a plan to throw suspicion onto Clancey.</p>', 32, 6, 25, '1969-03-29', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2255, 'The Space Pirates, Part Five', 20, '<p>Madeleine is revealed to be working with Caven, who comes up with a way to kill the Doctor and his friends whilst framing them for the piracy.</p>', 33, 6, 25, '1969-04-05', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2256, 'The Space Pirates, Part Six', 20, '<p>With Clancey and Issigri trapped aboard the LIZ, the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe try to convince Madeleine to help them before Caven destroys Ta.</p>', 34, 6, 25, '1969-04-12', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2257, 'The War Games, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe realise they have arrived in the trenches of the First World War, where the sinister General Smythe accuses them of espionage.</p>', 35, 6, 25, '1969-04-19', '/img/112/281939.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2258, 'The War Games, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Zoe manage to escape from Ransom and attempt to rescue Jamie from the military prison.</p>', 36, 6, 25, '1969-04-26', '/img/112/281941.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2259, 'The War Games, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends realise the area is divided into different time zones and decide to return to the château to obtain a map from Smythe.</p>', 37, 6, 25, '1969-05-03', '/img/112/281962.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2260, 'The War Games, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Zoe are transported to the control centre of the war games while Jamie and Lady Jennifer fall foul of American Revolution soldiers.</p>', 38, 6, 25, '1969-05-10', '/img/112/281964.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2261, 'The War Games, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to rescue Zoe and Carstairs while Jamie and Lady Jennifer try to convince the resistance of the true nature of Von Weich and the others.</p>', 39, 6, 25, '1969-05-17', '/img/112/281966.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2262, 'The War Games, Part Six', 20, '<p>The scientist examines the captured resistance fighters and realises Jamie is a new arrival on the planet while the Doctor, Zoe and Carstairs try to rescue their friends.</p>', 40, 6, 25, '1969-05-24', '/img/112/281967.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2263, 'The War Games, Part Seven', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Carstairs manage to return to the 1917 zone only to be captured by Smythe, who orders the Doctor executed.</p>', 41, 6, 25, '1969-05-31', '/img/112/281968.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2264, 'The War Games, Part Eight', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the processing machine have been taken by the Aliens but the resistance are making plans to attack the control centre.</p>', 42, 6, 25, '1969-06-07', '/img/112/281969.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2265, 'Spearhead from Space, Part One', 20, '<p>As the newly-regenerated Doctor arrives on Earth, so does the Nestene too.</p>', 1, 7, 25, '1970-01-03', '/img/112/281972.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2266, 'Spearhead from Space, Part Two', 20, '<p>UNIT\'s attempts to locate the meteorites are hampered by the mysterious plastic Autons, being constructed by Channing at a nearby factory, while the Doctor makes another attempt to escape from the hospital.</p>', 2, 7, 25, '1970-01-10', '/img/112/281973.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2267, 'Spearhead from Space, Part Three', 20, '<p>Ransome manages to escape from the plastics factory and alert UNIT, prompting the Doctor and the Brigadier to start an investigation.</p>', 3, 7, 25, '1970-01-17', '/img/114/285317.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2268, 'Spearhead from Space, Part Four', 20, '<p>With UNIT\'s investigation being blocked by the Replica of Scobie, the Doctor and Liz visit Madame Tussaud\'s to try and find out more as Channing prepares to activate the Autons.</p>', 4, 7, 25, '1970-01-24', '/img/114/285318.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2269, 'The Silurians, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Liz are summoned to the Wenley Moor Research Centre by the Brigadier, after several staff members suffer nervous breakdowns.</p>', 5, 7, 25, '1970-01-31', '/img/114/285319.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2270, 'The Silurians, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to convince people there are monsters in the caves, prompting Major Baker to start shooting at a reptile man.</p>', 6, 7, 25, '1970-02-07', '/img/114/285320.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2271, 'The Silurians, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Silurians contact Quinn for help in retrieving their fellow while the Doctor and the Brigadier organise a search of the moors.</p>', 7, 7, 25, '1970-02-14', '/img/114/285321.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2272, 'The Silurians, Part Four', 20, '<p>With Quinn dead, the Brigadier decides to take an armed party into the caves, prompting the Doctor to contact the Silurians himself.</p>', 8, 7, 25, '1970-02-21', '/img/114/285322.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2273, 'The Silurians, Part Five', 20, '<p>Worried about the Old Silurian\'s growing friendship with the Doctor, the Young Silurian has the scientist infect Baker with a virus and then release him.</p>', 9, 7, 25, '1970-02-28', '/img/114/285323.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2274, 'The Silurians, Part Six', 20, '<p>While the Doctor and Liz try to find a cure to the virus spread by Baker, the Young Silurian kills the Old Silurian and takes control of his people.</p>', 10, 7, 25, '1970-03-07', '/img/114/285324.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2275, 'The Silurians, Part Seven', 20, '<p>While Liz distributes the cure to the virus, the Doctor discovers the Silurians now plan to wipe out humanity by destroying the Van Allen Belt.</p>', 11, 7, 25, '1970-03-14', '/img/114/285325.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2276, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part One', 20, '<p>While the Brigadier investigates a loss of contact with Mars Probe 7, the Doctor realises signals coming from the probe are of extra-terrestrial origin.</p>', 12, 7, 25, '1970-03-21', '/img/114/285326.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2277, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Two', 20, '<p>UNIT retrieve the returned Recovery 7 but then Carrington hijacks it while the Doctor and Liz try to decode the signal he sent.</p>', 13, 7, 25, '1970-03-28', '/img/114/285327.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2278, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Three', 20, '<p>Carrington is holding the astronauts at a secret location but when he takes the Doctor, Liz and the Brigadier there they find they have been kidnapped.</p>', 14, 7, 25, '1970-04-04', '/img/114/285328.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2279, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Four', 20, '<p>Liz has been captured by Reegan\'s men and the Doctor begins to suspect Taltalian is more involved than he appeared.</p>', 15, 7, 25, '1970-04-11', '/img/114/285329.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2280, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor decides to take Recovery 7 back into space to search for the missing astronauts but Reegan sabotages the launch.</p>', 16, 7, 25, '1970-04-18', '/img/114/285331.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2281, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor speaks with the alien captain and learns the astronauts sent to Earth were ambassadors.However, before he can alert the authorities he is kidnapped by Reegan.</p>', 17, 7, 25, '1970-04-25', '/img/114/285332.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `nom`, `serie_id`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `duree`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2282, 'The Ambassadors of Death, Part Seven', 20, '<p>Carrington is planning to expose the aliens on live television and call for an interplanetary war and the Brigadier must rescue the Doctor and Liz in time to stop him.</p>', 18, 7, 25, '1970-05-02', '/img/114/285333.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2283, 'Inferno, Part One', 20, '<p>A dangerous experiment throws the Doctor into a doomed dimension</p>', 19, 7, 25, '1970-05-09', '/img/114/285335.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2284, 'Inferno, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor begins to suspect that penetrating the earth\'s crust will create more Primords but Stahlman sabotages the computer to stop him proving it.</p>', 20, 7, 25, '1970-05-16', '/img/114/285336.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2285, 'Inferno, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor finds himself in a parallel universe where Britain is a dictatorship and the Inferno Project is a slave labour camp policed by his friends\' counterparts.</p>', 21, 7, 25, '1970-05-23', '/img/114/285338.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2286, 'Inferno, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to convince the alternate Inferno staff that penetrating the earth\'s crust will cause a disaster but instead is imprisoned with an infected Bromley.</p>', 22, 7, 25, '1970-05-30', '/img/114/285339.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2287, 'Inferno, Part Five', 20, '<p>The earth\'s crust has been penetrated and, while the Doctor and Greg try to contain the disaster, the Doctor begins to realise the planet has passed the point of no return.</p>', 23, 7, 25, '1970-06-06', '/img/114/285340.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2288, 'Inferno, Part Six', 20, '<p>With the parallel earth doomed, the Doctor asks his friends\' counterparts to help him return to his own world but the Brigade Leader only sees the TARDIS as a means of escape.</p>', 24, 7, 25, '1970-06-13', '/img/114/285341.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2289, 'Inferno, Part Seven', 20, '<p>The Doctor is back in his own universe and must stop Stahlman before his earth suffers the same fate as the parallel one.</p>', 25, 7, 25, '1970-06-20', '/img/114/285342.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2290, 'Terror of the Autons, Part One', 20, '<p>When a Nestene Energy Unit is stolen and a radio telescope sabotaged, the Doctor is contacted by a Time Lord who tells him his old rival the Master is responsible.</p>', 1, 8, 25, '1971-01-02', '/img/114/285343.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2291, 'Terror of the Autons, Part Two', 20, '<p>Attempting to find out where Jo encountered the Master, the Doctor heads to the circus where he falls foul of Rossini.</p>', 2, 8, 25, '1971-01-09', '/img/114/285344.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2292, 'Terror of the Autons, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the Brigadier head to Farrel\'s factory but the Master and the Autons have already left and are distributing plastic daffodils around the country.</p>', 3, 8, 25, '1971-01-16', '/img/114/285345.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2293, 'Terror of the Autons, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor discovers the plastic daffodils are designed to fire a spray that asphyxiates people, causing havoc prior to the Nestene\'s arrival, but before he can alert anyone he and Jo are captured by the Master.</p>', 4, 8, 25, '1971-01-23', '/img/114/285346.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2294, 'The Mind of Evil, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo head to Stangmoor Prison to investigate the Keller Machine, which drains the evil impulses from prisoners\' minds, while UNIT are handling security at the first world peace conference.</p>', 5, 8, 25, '1971-01-30', '/img/114/285347.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2295, 'The Mind of Evil, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is recalled by UNIT to help investigate Cheng-Tiek\'s murder but is unaware that Chin-Lee is under the control of the Master.</p>', 6, 8, 25, '1971-02-06', '/img/114/285348.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2296, 'The Mind of Evil, Part Three', 20, '<p>Realising Chin-Lee has been using the power of the Keller Machine to carry out assassinations, the Doctor heads back to Stangmoor, only to find the Master has teamed up with Mailer to stage another riot.</p>', 7, 8, 25, '1971-02-13', '/img/114/285349.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2297, 'The Mind of Evil, Part Four', 20, '<p>With the Doctor and Jo being held prisoner, the Master convinces Mailer to help him steal the Thunderbolt.</p>', 8, 8, 25, '1971-02-20', '/img/114/285350.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2298, 'The Mind of Evil, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor is forced to help the Master control the mind parasite while Yates finds out where the Thunderbolt has been taken only to be captured by the Master\'s men.</p>', 9, 8, 25, '1971-02-27', '/img/114/285351.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2299, 'The Mind of Evil, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Brigadier has recaptured Stangmoor but the Master still has control of the Thunderbolt and the Doctor must find a way to stop him and destroy the Keller Machine.</p>', 10, 8, 25, '1971-03-06', '/img/114/285352.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2300, 'The Claws of Axos, Part One', 20, '<p>When a mysterious object lands near the Nuton power complex, UNIT investigate and encounter the Axons, a group of aliens who offer the mineral axonite, which can duplicate matter, as a gift.</p>', 11, 8, 25, '1971-03-13', '/img/46/115265.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2301, 'The Claws of Axos, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Winser begin to analyse axonite while Chinn plots to secure its use exclusively for Britain.</p>', 12, 8, 25, '1971-03-20', '/img/46/115332.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2302, 'The Claws of Axos, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo are being held prisoner by Axos while Chinn is forced to organise the worldwide distribution of axonite and the Master returns to the power complex to try and steal the TARDIS.</p>', 13, 8, 25, '1971-03-27', '/img/46/115653.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2303, 'The Claws of Axos, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo escape from Axos but then the Doctor offers the Master a deal:if he helps him repair the TARDIS, they can flee Earth together.</p>', 14, 8, 25, '1971-04-03', '/img/46/115669.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2304, 'Colony in Space, Part One', 20, '<p>The Time Lords takes control of the TARDIS and the Doctor and Jo arrive on a Earth Colony in the 25th Century, where a ruthless mining company are using a dinosaur-like creature to force the colonists to leave the planet. Where the Doctor and Jo learn that The Master is on the planet and is in search of a doomsday weapon that is hidden somewhere on the planet.</p>', 15, 8, 25, '1971-04-10', '/img/57/143900.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2305, 'Colony in Space, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor discovers an Interplanetary Mining Corporation ship has landed on the planet in order to mine its duralinium, while Norton begins causing trouble at the colony.</p>', 16, 8, 25, '1971-04-17', '/img/57/143901.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2306, 'Colony in Space, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor makes it back to the colony and warns Ashe what Dent is up to but when Jo and Winton try to find proof they are captured.</p>', 17, 8, 25, '1971-04-24', '/img/57/143917.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2307, 'Colony in Space, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor descends into the Primitive city to try and find Jo while the colonists receive a visit from the Adjudicator.</p>', 18, 8, 25, '1971-05-01', '/img/57/143920.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2308, 'Colony in Space, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Master offers to help the colonists in exchange for information on the Primitive city and forces the Doctor to act as a guide by taking Jo hostage.</p>', 19, 8, 25, '1971-05-08', '/img/57/143942.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2309, 'Colony in Space, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the Master are taken into the Primitive city, where the Master hopes to find the doomsday weapon, while Dent forces the colonists to leave the planet even though their ship is likely to explode.</p>', 20, 8, 25, '1971-05-15', '/img/58/145502.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2310, 'The Dæmons, Part One', 20, '<p>The Master raises the Devil. The Doctor becomes a wizard.</p>', 21, 8, 25, '1971-05-22', '/img/63/157890.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2311, 'The Dæmons, Part Two', 20, '<p>With the Doctor frozen by the energy release from the barrow, Jo calls Yates and Benton for help, but when the Brigadier tries to join them he finds the village surrounded by a heat barrier.</p>', 22, 8, 25, '1971-05-29', '/img/63/157891.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2312, 'The Dæmons, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor explains to his friends that the Master is trying to gain the power of the last of the Daemons, a race who influenced Earth\'s development, while the Master brings the rest of the village under his control.</p>', 23, 8, 25, '1971-06-05', '/img/63/157894.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2313, 'The Dæmons, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Master orders Bert to set a trap for the Doctor at the village while a concussed Jo makes for the cavern.</p>', 24, 8, 25, '1971-06-12', '/img/63/159734.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2314, 'The Dæmons, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Master decides to sacrifice Jo to Azal and when the Doctor and his friends try to intervene they come under attack from Bok.</p>', 25, 8, 25, '1971-06-19', '/img/63/159736.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2315, 'Day of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>When someone tries to assassinate diplomat Sir Reginald Styles, UNIT investigate the possibility his attacker came from the future.</p>', 1, 9, 25, '1972-01-01', '/img/67/167552.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2316, 'Day of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>Jo uses the guerrillas\' time machine to travel to the 22nd century where the Controller tricks her into telling the Daleks where she\'s come from.</p>', 2, 9, 25, '1972-01-08', '/img/67/167594.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2317, 'Day of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor forces the guerrillas to take him to the 22nd century where he is soon captured by the Controller.</p>', 3, 9, 25, '1972-01-15', '/img/67/167599.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2318, 'Day of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>The guerrillas infiltrate the Daleks\' base to rescue the Doctor and Jo and ask them to return to their own time and alter history before the 20th century is plunged into a Third World War.</p>', 4, 9, 25, '1972-01-22', '/img/67/167609.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2319, 'The Curse of Peladon, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo arrive on the medieval planet Peladon, where the Doctor is mistaken for the Earth Delegate of the Galactic Federation and Jo is mistaken for a princess. Where the Doctor uncovers a conspiracy, as he exposes the evil scheme of the high-priest Hepesh who bids to prevent King Peladon from joining the galactic Federation.</p>', 5, 9, 25, '1972-01-29', '/img/67/167617.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2320, 'The Curse of Peladon, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is convinced the Ice Warriors are trying to sabotage the conference but his attempts to prove it see him accused of sacrilege.</p>', 6, 9, 25, '1972-02-05', '/img/67/167630.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2321, 'The Curse of Peladon, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor is sentenced to fight Grun to the death and his attempt to escape leads to an encounter with Aggedor.</p>', 7, 9, 25, '1972-02-12', '/img/67/167641.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2322, 'The Curse of Peladon, Part Four', 20, '<p>Hepesh\'s plan has been exposed but he is still determined to prevent Peladon joining the Galactic Federation by leading a rebellion against the King.</p>', 8, 9, 25, '1972-02-19', '/img/67/167654.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2323, 'The Sea Devils, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo visit the Master at his island prison where the Doctor becomes curious about a number of ships sinking in the area.</p>', 9, 9, 25, '1972-02-26', '/img/84/212317.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2324, 'The Sea Devils, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo are trapped on the fort by a Sea Devil while the Master convinces Trenchard to help him steal some electronic components.</p>', 10, 9, 25, '1972-03-04', '/img/84/212446.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2325, 'The Sea Devils, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor is held prisoner by Trenchard while the Master attempts to contact the Sea Devils.</p>', 11, 9, 25, '1972-03-11', '/img/85/212552.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2326, 'The Sea Devils, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Sea Devils attack the island prison and rescue the Master, prompting the Doctor to venture underwater to try and contact them.</p>', 12, 9, 25, '1972-03-18', '/img/85/212556.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2327, 'The Sea Devils, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor is taken to the Sea Devils\' underwater colony where he tries to make peace with the creatures, only for the navy to attack the base.</p>', 13, 9, 25, '1972-03-25', '/img/85/212557.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2328, 'The Sea Devils, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Sea Devils take over the naval base and the Doctor is forced to help the Master find a way to revive their colony.</p>', 14, 9, 25, '1972-04-01', '/img/85/212558.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2329, 'The Mutants, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo arrive on the planet Solos, on a assignment by the Time Lords. Where the Doctor and Jo learn that the native Solonians are mutating into ant-like mutant creatures and they uncover a conspiracy, where the evil Marshal of the Earth Empire plots to rule Solos for himself and plans to convert Solos atmosphere, since the planet\'s atmosphere is poisonous, so the planet can be colonized by the humans and he plans to wipe out all the mutated Solonians, who are evolving into a advanced super race.</p>', 15, 9, 25, '1972-04-08', '/img/88/222435.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2330, 'The Mutants, Part Two', 20, '<p>Ky transports himself and Jo down to Solos and the Marshal only agrees to help her if the Doctor assists Professor Jaeger in altering Solos\' atmosphere.</p>', 16, 9, 25, '1972-04-15', '/img/88/222436.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2331, 'The Mutants, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Varan travel down to Solos to search for Jo and Ky but the Marshal orders his men to pursue them.</p>', 17, 9, 25, '1972-04-22', '/img/88/222473.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2332, 'The Mutants, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends are led to safety by Professor Sondergaard, who tries to help the Doctor translate the tablets.</p>', 18, 9, 25, '1972-04-29', '/img/88/222475.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2333, 'The Mutants, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Marshal\'s premature use of Jaeger\'s experiment is threatening to destroy Solos\' atmosphere and the Doctor returns to Skybase to try and correct the damage.</p>', 19, 9, 25, '1972-05-06', '/img/88/222476.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2334, 'The Mutants, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor is forced to help the Marshal cover up his actions with the Investigator but Jo and the others attempt to escape to expose him.</p>', 20, 9, 25, '1972-05-13', '/img/88/222478.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2335, 'The Time Monster, Part One', 20, '<p>UNIT are invited to observe a demonstration of the new TOMTIT machine, unaware its creator, Professor Thascales, is actually the Master.</p>', 21, 9, 25, '1972-05-20', '/img/114/285356.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2336, 'The Time Monster, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor realises the Master is trying to harness the power of Kronos, last of the Chronovores, but is unaware Percival is harbouring him at the institute.</p>', 22, 9, 25, '1972-05-27', '/img/114/285357.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2337, 'The Time Monster, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Master enlists the help of Krasis to control Kronos while Yates tries to bring the TARDIS to the institute only to come under attack from dangers from the past.</p>', 23, 9, 25, '1972-06-03', '/img/114/285358.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2338, 'The Time Monster, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Master prepares to travel back to Atlantis but the Doctor links his TARDIS to the Master\'s to try and stop him.</p>', 24, 9, 25, '1972-06-10', '/img/114/285360.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2339, 'The Time Monster, Part Five', 20, '<p>Both TARDISes reach Atlantis, where the Doctor befriends King Dalios while the Master enlists the help of Queen Galleia to try and obtain the crystal of Kronos.</p>', 25, 9, 25, '1972-06-17', '/img/114/285361.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2340, 'The Time Monster, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor enters the labyrinth to try and protect Jo from the minotaur but the Master has seized control of Atlantis and prepares to summon Kronos again.</p>', 26, 9, 25, '1972-06-24', '/img/114/285362.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2341, 'The Three Doctors, Part One', 20, '<p>The 10th Anniversary Serial has three incarnations of the Doctor meeting up to face the evil Omega in a universe of antimatter.</p>', 1, 10, 25, '1972-12-30', '/img/114/285364.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2342, 'The Three Doctors, Part Two', 20, '<p>The third Doctor and Jo find themselves on an artificial world inside the black hole while the second Doctor tries to find a way to control the organism.</p>', 2, 10, 25, '1973-01-06', '/img/114/285365.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2343, 'The Three Doctors, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Time Lord Omega reveals himself to the third Doctor along with plans for vengeance against his own kind.</p>', 3, 10, 25, '1973-01-13', '/img/114/285373.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2344, 'The Three Doctors, Part Four', 20, '<p>Omega reveals the purpose behind bringing the Doctor to his antimatter world, but the Doctor(s) discover a startling fact about Omega that he didn\'t know himself and eventually strike a bargain.</p>', 4, 10, 25, '1973-01-20', '/img/114/285383.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2345, 'Carnival of Monsters, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to test his new dematerialisation circuit by taking Jo to Metebelis Three but instead the TARDIS arrives in the hold of a 1920s cargo ship.</p>', 5, 10, 25, '1973-01-27', '/img/114/285389.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2346, 'Carnival of Monsters, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo attempt to find a way out of the Scope but, when Vorg attempts to entertain the Minorans, the crew of the Bernice suddenly become a lot more dangerous.</p>', 6, 10, 25, '1973-02-03', '/img/114/285391.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2347, 'Carnival of Monsters, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo return to the Bernice to try and aid their escape but find themselves pursued by the Drashigs.</p>', 7, 10, 25, '1973-02-10', '/img/114/285392.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2348, 'Carnival of Monsters, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor escapes from the Scope and joins forces with Vorg to try and save its inhabitants but Kalik is still determined to use the Drashigs to start a rebellion.</p>', 8, 10, 25, '1973-02-17', '/img/114/285404.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2349, 'Frontier in Space, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo discover The Master and the Ogrons are the masterminds behind the Galactic war between the Earth Federation and the Reptillian Draconian Empire and the Master has framed The Doctor and Jo as spies working for the Draconians. Only to discover The Master is also working with the Doctor\'s greatest enemies, The Daleks, who are also behind the galactic war.</p>', 9, 10, 25, '1973-02-24', '/img/114/285414.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2350, 'Frontier in Space, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo are taken to Earth, where both humans and Draconians believe them to be a spy for the other side.</p>', 10, 10, 25, '1973-03-03', '/img/114/285426.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2351, 'Frontier in Space, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor is sentenced to life imprisonment at a lunar penal colony while Jo encounters an old enemy.</p>', 11, 10, 25, '1973-03-10', '/img/114/285428.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2352, 'Frontier in Space, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Master rescues the Doctor from the lunar penal colony, aiming to take him and Jo to the Ogrons\' planet, and the Doctor\'s attempt to escape leaves him stranded in space.</p>', 12, 10, 25, '1973-03-17', '/img/114/285803.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2353, 'Frontier in Space, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Jo and the Master are taken to Draconia, where the Doctor tries to convince the Draconians of the truth. But then the Ogrons attack.</p>', 13, 10, 25, '1973-03-24', '/img/114/285804.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2354, 'Frontier in Space, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Williams and the Draconian Prince head to the Ogrons\' planet to find evidence of the Master\'s actions but the Master tricks Jo into leading them into a trap.</p>', 14, 10, 25, '1973-03-31', '/img/114/285805.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2355, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS lands on the jungle planet Spiridon, where the Doctor has fallen into a coma, where The Doctor has requested the Time Lords to pilot the TARDIS, so he and Jo can follow the Daleks to their base. Where Jo learns the Dalek\'s base has been located on Spiridon where the Daleks are attempting to discover the secrets of Invisibilty and create a bacterial virus in their goal of universal conquest. Where The Doctor, recovered from his coma and Jo are joined by a task-force of Thals and a native Spiridon named Wester, Where they not only set out to stop The Daleks evil plot, they also discover a army of 12,000 Daleks are in suspended animation and are waiting to be revived to begin their universal conquest and claim themselves as the supreme rulers of the galaxy.</p>', 15, 10, 25, '1973-04-07', '/img/114/285806.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2356, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is captured by the Daleks, while Jo is rescued by a friendly Spridon named Wester.</p>', 16, 10, 25, '1973-04-14', '/img/114/285807.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2357, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Codal escape from their cell and meet up with the Thal commandos who are trying to get into the Dalek base.</p>', 17, 10, 25, '1973-04-21', '/img/114/285809.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2358, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends escape from the Dalek base, prompting the Daleks to devise a plan to wipe them out.</p>', 18, 10, 25, '1973-04-28', '/img/114/285810.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2359, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends ambush two Daleks as part of their planet to get back into the city but the Daleks are on the verge of unleashing their virus.</p>', 19, 10, 25, '1973-05-05', '/img/114/285811.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2360, 'Planet of the Daleks, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends prepare to refreeze the Dalek army but the Dalek Supreme has arrived on the planet determined to destroy them all.</p>', 20, 10, 25, '1973-05-12', '/img/114/285812.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2361, 'The Green Death, Part One', 20, '<p>While the Doctor plans a holiday to Metebelis Three, Jo and the Brigadier are intrigued by a mysterious death at a coal mine in Llanfairfach, which is being blamed on local company Global Chemicals.</p>', 21, 10, 25, '1973-05-19', '/img/114/285813.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2362, 'The Green Death, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the Brigadier attempt to rescue Jo and Bert from the mine but Global Chemicals prove distinctly uncooperative.</p>', 22, 10, 25, '1973-05-26', '/img/114/285818.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2363, 'The Green Death, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Jo manage to escape from the mine with a maggot egg but Stevens is determined to stop them analysing it.</p>', 23, 10, 25, '1973-06-02', '/img/114/285828.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2364, 'The Green Death, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Brigadier calls in a full UNIT force to deal with the giant maggots while the Doctor infiltrates Global Chemicals to find out what is really going on.</p>', 24, 10, 25, '1973-06-09', '/img/114/285833.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2365, 'The Green Death, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor manages to escape from BOSS with help from Yates and discovers Cliff has been infected by a giant maggot.</p>', 25, 10, 25, '1973-06-16', '/img/114/285837.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2366, 'The Green Death, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to destroy the giant maggots and cure Cliff but the real threat is BOSS, who is poised to take over all the world\'s computers.</p>', 26, 10, 25, '1973-06-23', '/img/114/285860.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2367, 'The Time Warrior, Part One', 20, '<p>The Brigadier asks the Doctor to investigate the disappearance of several scientists, only for him to find they have been abducted back in time.</p>', 1, 11, 25, '1973-12-15', '/img/114/285861.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2368, 'The Time Warrior, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor tracks the missing scientists to Irongron\'s castle, where Linx is using them to repair his spaceship and construct advanced weapons for Irongron.</p>', 2, 11, 25, '1973-12-22', '/img/114/285863.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2369, 'The Time Warrior, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor escapes the castle with Sarah and Hal and must persuade Sir Edward to trust him before Irongron launches an attack on them.</p>', 3, 11, 25, '1973-12-29', '/img/114/285868.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2370, 'The Time Warrior, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to return the scientists to their own time, before Linx tries to use his spaceship and destroys the entire castle.</p>', 4, 11, 25, '1974-01-05', '/img/114/285870.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2371, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah return to London in the present day only to find the city strangely deserted, while nearby UNIT are dealing with a series of monster appearances.</p>', 5, 11, 25, '1974-01-12', '/img/114/285884.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2372, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah returns to present-day Earth, where they find London has been evacuated, and Dinosaurs are on the loose and they are mistaken for looters. Assisting U.N.I.T in the emergency, The Doctor and Sarah discovers corrupt politician Sir Charles Grover MP, renegade scientists Butler and Professor Whitaker and military officer General Finch are using a time machine to bring the dinosaurs from the past to the present as part of they scheme to bring the human race back to a \"Golden Age\" before the world was polluted.</p>', 6, 11, 25, '1974-01-19', '/img/114/285890.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2373, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Three', 20, '<p>Yates sabotages the Doctor\'s equipment to stop him finding the location of Whitaker\'s base but then the tyrannosaur escapes, placing Sarah in danger.</p>', 7, 11, 25, '1974-01-26', '/img/114/285892.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2374, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Four', 20, '<p>Sarah attempts to find a way off the spaceship while the Doctor tries to track down the source of the time displacements.</p>', 8, 11, 25, '1974-02-02', '/img/114/285893.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2375, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor has been framed as the monster maker by Finch and is on the run from the army, while Sarah attempts to alert UNIT to what Grover is up to.</p>', 9, 11, 25, '1974-02-09', '/img/114/285894.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2376, 'Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor is rescued from Finch by the Brigadier and Benton and tries to persuade them to stop Grover before millions of people are erased from history.</p>', 10, 11, 25, '1974-02-16', '/img/114/285895.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2377, 'Death to the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>As the TARDIS heads to the paradise planet Florana where the Doctor and Sarah go for a holiday, the TARDIS goes off-course and arrives on the barren planet Exxilon, where the TARDIS is loosing power. The Doctor and Sarah finds a group of humans and Daleks are searching for Parrinium, a mineral which is the only antidote to a space plague. Both parties encounter the native people and trouble ensues. In an attempt to find what caused the power-loss, the Doctor, chased by the Daleks, enter the Exxilon\'s lost city to be able to stop the power draining phenomenon.</p>', 11, 11, 25, '1974-02-23', '/img/114/285912.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2378, 'Death to the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the MSC crew join forces with the Daleks to mine the parrinium, only to come under attack from the Exxilons.</p>', 12, 11, 25, '1974-03-02', '/img/114/285919.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2379, 'Death to the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah meet up with Bellal, who helps them escape from the Daleks and explains the origin of the City.</p>', 13, 11, 25, '1974-03-09', '/img/114/285922.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2380, 'Death to the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Bellal continue to penetrate the City\'s defences while Sarah and Jill try to stop the Daleks leaving with the parrinium.</p>', 14, 11, 25, '1974-03-16', '/img/114/285932.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2381, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part One', 20, '<p>Returning to the medieval planet Peladon (50 years after \"The Curse of Peladon\") The Doctor and Sarah find King Peladon\'s daughter Queen Thalira has inherited the throne and the galactic Federation is at war with Galaxy Five and The Federation requires the mineral Trisilicate that will end the war. Only to discover the miners led by the mad rebel Ettis are rebelling and refusing to work, as the ghost of the loyal best Aggedor is frightening and killing off Miners, only to discover the ghost of Aggedor is a holographic projection and the culprits are a task-force of renegade Ice Warriors led by Commander Azaxyr and traitorous federation mining engineer Eckersley who have betrayed the Federation to Galaxy Five.</p>', 15, 11, 25, '1974-03-23', '/img/114/285934.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2382, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is rescued by Gebek, prompting him to try and help the miners, but his advice results in Ettis launching another attack on the armoury.</p>', 16, 11, 25, '1974-03-30', '/img/114/285938.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2383, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah pacify Aggedor and the Doctor encourages the Queen to make peace with the miners, but Ortron soon has him under arrest again.</p>', 17, 11, 25, '1974-04-06', '/img/114/285942.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2384, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Ice Warriors take control of the planet and force the miners to return to work but Ettis takes the opportunity to try and destroy the citadel.</p>', 18, 11, 25, '1974-04-13', '/img/114/285948.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2385, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part Five', 20, '<p>Sarah and Alpha Centauri decide to try and alert the Federation to what the Ice Warriors are up to but first they have to escape from the throne room.</p>', 19, 11, 25, '1974-04-20', '/img/114/285950.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2386, 'The Monster of Peladon, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor turns the Aggedor spirit against the Ice Warriors to aid the Peladonians in their battle but Eckersley attacks him with the security system.</p>', 20, 11, 25, '1974-04-27', '/img/114/286491.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2387, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part One', 20, '<p>While the Doctor carries out an investigation into ESP, Mike Yates asks Sarah to look into some strange goings on at a meditation centre he\'s attending.</p>', 21, 11, 25, '1974-05-04', '/img/114/286492.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2388, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part Two', 20, '<p>Lupton forms an alliance with the spider to steal the Doctor\'s blue crystal, while Sarah and Mike attempt to alert people to what they\'ve seen.</p>', 22, 11, 25, '1974-05-11', '/img/114/286493.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2389, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah head to the meditation centre to try and get the crystal back while Lupton prepares to return it to Metebelis Three.But all their plans are disrupted when it is stolen by Tommy.</p>', 23, 11, 25, '1974-05-18', '/img/114/286494.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2390, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part Four', 20, '<p>Sarah is captured by the spiders\' guards while the Doctor tries to help Arak and the others strike back against the spiders.</p>', 24, 11, 25, '1974-05-25', '/img/114/286495.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2391, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor escapes from the spiders\' larder only to encounter the Great One, while Sarah makes a deal with the Queen Spider.</p>', 25, 11, 25, '1974-06-01', '/img/114/286496.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2392, 'Planet of the Spiders, Part Six', 20, '<p>K\'Anpo persuades the Doctor he must face his fear and return the crystal to the Great One.But first they need to get past Barnes and his men.</p>', 26, 11, 25, '1974-06-08', '/img/114/286497.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2393, 'Robot, Part One', 20, '<p>Can the Doctor, now in his fourth incarnation. Recover from his post regenerative trauma to save the Earth from Think Tank and their plot for world domination.</p>', 1, 12, 25, '1974-12-28', '/img/85/213007.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2394, 'Robot, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah become convinced Think Tank are behind the electronic component thefts but are unable to stop them carrying out another raid.</p>', 2, 12, 25, '1975-01-04', '/img/85/213008.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2395, 'Robot, Part Three', 20, '<p>Sarah and Kettlewell infiltrate an SRS meeting to try and find out what Miss Winters is up to but there is a surprise in store.</p>', 3, 12, 25, '1975-01-11', '/img/85/213011.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2396, 'Robot, Part Four', 20, '<p>UNIT attempt to get into the bunker to stop Miss Winters setting off the world\'s nuclear missiles but first they have to get past the K1.</p>', 4, 12, 25, '1975-01-18', '/img/85/213013.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2397, 'The Ark in Space, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor\'s attempt to give Harry a trip in the TARDIS sees the two of them and Sarah arriving onboard a space station in the far future, with some rather deadly security mechanisms.</p>', 5, 12, 25, '1975-01-25', '/img/85/213020.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2398, 'The Ark in Space, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Harry revive the Ark\'s medtech, Vira, to help Sarah.But when station commander Noah is revived, he becomes suspicious of the newcomers.</p>', 6, 12, 25, '1975-02-01', '/img/85/213021.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2399, 'The Ark in Space, Part Three', 20, '<p>Knowing that Noah has been infected by the Wirrn, the Doctor persuades Vira to halt the reviving of her people, knowing it will place them in danger as well.</p>', 7, 12, 25, '1975-02-08', '/img/85/213023.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2400, 'The Ark in Space, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor tries to protect the humans still in cryogenic suspension from the Wirrn, who are determined to use Earth as their new breeding ground.</p>', 8, 12, 25, '1975-02-15', '/img/85/213266.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2401, 'The Sontaran Experiment, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Sarah and Harry teleports to Earth to ensure the planet is safe for the survivors on-board Nerva Beacon to return to Earth and re-inhabit their world. Only to find a Sontaran named Styre has captured a group of humans and conducting experiments on them to discover the human body\'s weaknesses, as part of the Sontaran\'s goal for domination of the galaxy.</p>', 9, 12, 25, '1975-02-22', '/img/53/133251.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2402, 'The Sontaran Experiment, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor learns that Styre has been experimenting on the Galsec crewmembers to pave the way for a Sontaran invasion of Earth and decides the only way to halt his plans is to challenge him to a duel.</p>', 10, 12, 25, '1975-03-01', '/img/53/133255.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2403, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his companions are sent to the planet Skaro by the Time Lords to prevent the creation of the Daleks.</p>', 11, 12, 25, '1975-03-08', '/img/85/214328.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2404, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Harry are taken to the Kaled bunker where Davros is preparing to demonstrate the Daleks, while Sarah is captured by the Thals and taken to their city as a slave worker.</p>', 12, 12, 25, '1975-03-15', '/img/85/214330.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2405, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Harry head to the Kaled city to alert the authorities to Davros\' plans while Sarah and Sevrin are forced to work on the completion of the Thals\' rocket.</p>', 13, 12, 25, '1975-03-22', '/img/85/214332.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2406, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor fails to prevent the Thals from destroying the Kaled city but they don\'t have long to enjoy their victory before the Daleks attack.</p>', 14, 12, 25, '1975-03-29', '/img/85/214333.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2407, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor is forced to give Davros full details of future Dalek victories but opposition to Davros\' plans is growing among the Kaleds and soon there is open rebellion.</p>', 15, 12, 25, '1975-04-05', '/img/85/214335.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2408, 'Genesis of the Daleks, Part Six', 20, '<p>Gharman tries to convince the Kaleds to vote against the Dalek project but Davros has a trick up his sleeve, while the Doctor works to destroy the tape recording of Dalek victory and the Thals plan an intervention of their own.</p>', 16, 12, 25, '1975-04-12', '/img/85/214334.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2409, 'Revenge of the Cybermen, Part One', 20, '<p>The Time Ring returns The Doctor, Sarah and Harry to Nerva Beacon thousands of years before they left. Where the Doctor, Sarah and Harry find the Beacon\'s crew have been wiped out by a space plague, only to discover the crew have been murdered by a cybermat and the culprits are the Cybermen and geologist Professor Kellman who bid to wipe out \"Voga\" a planet of gold, home of the subterranean Vogans who defeated the Cybermen in a war.</p>', 17, 12, 25, '1975-04-19', '/img/89/223756.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2410, 'Revenge of the Cybermen, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor transmits Sarah and Harry down to Voga to cure Sarah of the Cybermat\'s poison but Kellman\'s sabotage means he is unable to bring them back.</p>', 18, 12, 25, '1975-04-26', '/img/89/223807.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2411, 'Revenge of the Cybermen, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Cybermen force the Doctor, Stevenson and Lester to carry bombs to the centre of Voga while Sarah, Harry and Tyrum decide to contact Vorus.</p>', 19, 12, 25, '1975-05-03', '/img/89/223808.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2412, 'Revenge of the Cybermen, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Harry and Lester try to destroy the Cybermen\'s relay device, while the Vogans prepare to destroy Nerva even though Sarah is still on board.</p>', 20, 12, 25, '1975-05-10', '/img/89/223809.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2413, 'Terror of the Zygons, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Sarah and Harry are summoned back to Earth, where the Brigadier asks them to investigate the destruction of a series of North Sea oil rigs.</p>', 1, 13, 25, '1975-08-30', '/img/114/286519.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2414, 'Terror of the Zygons, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Zygon traps the Doctor and Sarah in a decompression chamber while Harry is taken to the aliens\' underwater ship.</p>', 2, 13, 25, '1975-09-06', '/img/114/286520.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2415, 'Terror of the Zygons, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and the Brigadier begin to realise who the Zygon imposters among them are while Sarah discovers a secret tunnel to the underwater ship.</p>', 3, 13, 25, '1975-09-13', '/img/114/286521.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2416, 'Terror of the Zygons, Part Four', 20, '<p>UNIT attempt to track down the Zygon ship while Broton prepares to have the Skarasen attack London.</p>', 4, 13, 25, '1975-09-20', '/img/114/286522.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2417, 'Planet of Evil, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah answer a distress call and find themselves on Zeta Minor, the last planet of the known universe, where a Morestran expedition has gone missing.</p>', 5, 13, 25, '1975-09-27', '/img/114/286523.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2418, 'Planet of Evil, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor realises that Zeta Minor lies on the boundary between the universes of matter and anti-matter and something on the planet won\'t let the Morestrans leave.</p>', 6, 13, 25, '1975-10-04', '/img/114/286524.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2419, 'Planet of Evil, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor makes a deal with the Anti-Matter Beast to return all the anti-matter to the planet but Sorenson is determined to continue his research.</p>', 7, 13, 25, '1975-10-11', '/img/114/286529.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2420, 'Planet of Evil, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor tries to convince Sorenson to sacrifice himself for the rest of the crew but Salamar\'s attempt to deal with the situation causes their problem to multiply.</p>', 8, 13, 25, '1975-10-18', '/img/114/286531.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2421, 'Pyramids of Mars, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah are drawn off course and, instead of UNIT HQ, they arrive on the same site in 1911.</p>', 9, 13, 25, '1975-10-25', '/img/114/286532.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2422, 'Pyramids of Mars, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Sarah and Laurence try to find a way to sever Sutekh\'s link to the mummies while poacher Ernie Clements finds the priory surrounded by a forcefield.</p>', 10, 13, 25, '1975-11-01', '/img/114/286534.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2423, 'Pyramids of Mars, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah try to destroy Sutekh\'s rocket but the Osiran\'s mental powers prove too great for them.</p>', 11, 13, 25, '1975-11-08', '/img/114/286537.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2424, 'Pyramids of Mars, Part Four', 20, '<p>Sutekh forces the Doctor to transport Scarman and a mummy to Mars, where the Doctor and Sarah try to stop them destroying the Eye of Horus.</p>', 12, 13, 25, '1975-11-15', '/img/114/286538.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2425, 'The Android Invasion, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah return to Earth in the present day to find a strangely deserted village and woods stalked by white-clad figures.</p>', 13, 13, 25, '1975-11-22', '/img/114/286543.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2426, 'The Android Invasion, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor suspects Crayford brought something to Earth in his rocket, as he and Sarah find themselves hunted by UNIT.</p>', 14, 13, 25, '1975-11-29', '/img/114/286544.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2427, 'The Android Invasion, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor is captured by Styggron and left to die in the destruction of the fake village but Sarah escapes from the disorientation chamber to try and rescue him.</p>', 15, 13, 25, '1975-12-06', '/img/114/286549.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:08', '2019-12-19 02:15:08'),
(2428, 'The Android Invasion, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah reach Earth and try to warn the research centre about the Kraal invasion before Styggron unleashes his virus.</p>', 16, 13, 25, '1975-12-13', '/img/114/286551.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2429, 'The Brain of Morbius, Part One', 20, '<p>The Tardis lands on the bleak planet Karn, in a spaceship graveyard, where The Doctor and Sarah find a evil scientist called Doctor Solon is constructing a new body for the brain of a evil time lord known as Morbius, whom The Doctor thought was executed by the high council on Gallifrey. Where Morbius with his new body plots to rule the galaxy.</p>', 17, 13, 25, '1976-01-03', '/img/114/286552.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2430, 'The Brain of Morbius, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Sisterhood prepare to sacrifice the Doctor to the Sacred Flame and Sarah is injured while rescuing him.</p>', 18, 13, 25, '1976-01-10', '/img/114/286558.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2431, 'The Brain of Morbius, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor attempts to restore the Sacred Flame to prove his good intentions to the Sisterhood, while Solon prepares to connect the brain of Morbius to his body.</p>', 19, 13, 25, '1976-01-17', '/img/114/286566.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2432, 'The Brain of Morbius, Part Four', 20, '<p>Morbius goes on the rampage, forcing the Doctor and Solon to team up to try and bring him back under control.</p>', 20, 13, 25, '1976-01-24', '/img/114/286571.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2433, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part One', 20, '<p>Members of the World Ecology Bureau discover a centuries-old seed pod buried deep in Antarctica\'s permafrost. It seems to be still alive, growing without soil. They transmit a photo to London where Richard Dunbar of the W.E.B. shares it with the Doctor. Wary of what it might be, the Doctor immediately flies down with Sarah. They don\'t know that Dunbar is a leak in the bureau and has tipped off the discovery to a rich plant fanatic named Harrison Chase. Chase sends a thug and a plant expert down to verify the discovery and fetch it back by any means possible. But before anyone arrives, the pod hatches and the tendril-like life form within attaches itself to one of the men, turning him green. It\'s as The Doctor feared: they\'re dealing with a Krynoid.</p>', 21, 13, 25, '1976-01-31', '/img/114/286578.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2434, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part Two', 20, '<p>With a killer Krynoid on the loose, the Doctor, Sarah and the last surviving member of the expedition concentrate on hunting it down, unmindful of Chase\'s men who, once they learn of the second Krynoid pod (which always travel through space in pairs), work to obtain it and eliminate all possible witnesses.</p>', 22, 13, 25, '1976-02-07', '/img/114/286582.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2435, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part Three', 20, '<p>Surviving two attempts to end their lives, the Doctor and Sarah seek the identity of the plant fanatic who ordered the hit on the arctic base, pursuing their only lead - a commissioned painting of a rare flower left in the boot of a car. Chase, meanwhile, is doing all he can to encourage the hatching of the Krynoid pod.</p>', 23, 13, 25, '1976-02-14', '/img/114/286584.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `nom`, `serie_id`, `resume`, `numero`, `saison`, `duree`, `premiere`, `urlImage`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2436, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part Four', 20, '<p>Sarah is saved from a Krynoid fate and runs off, but the same can\'t be said for one of Chase\'s men. Not only is he simultaneously devoured and transformed, his fascinated employer will do all he can to encourage the process. The Doctor gets introduced to Chase\'s grinder and compost acceleration chamber, which promises him a painful yet swift death en route to making him one with nature, via the garden\'s nutrient pump. The situation has finally gone too far for Dunbar, who outs his own involvement in this matter and stands up to Chase, only to come face to face with a fully developed Krynoid.</p>', 24, 13, 25, '1976-02-21', '/img/114/286589.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2437, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part Five', 20, '<p>In the interest in self-preservation, Chase\'s men side with The Doctor against the Krynoid, but the Krynoid - now bigger than the Chase Mansion - invites The Doctor to join it, promising to leave the others alone if he does. People within a mile of the Chase Estate, however, start getting strangled by their plants, while Chase, snapping photos of the Krynoid, has a significant one-on-one encounter with it.</p>', 25, 13, 25, '1976-02-28', '/img/114/286590.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2438, 'The Seeds of Doom, Part Six', 20, '<p>Chase is obviously under Krynoid control. The Doctor suspects possession but, with the mountainous Krynoid nearing maturity and whacking the mansion to pieces, he concerns himself with the bigger picture and orders the mansion - with Sarah and him still inside - to be bombed.</p>', 26, 13, 25, '1976-03-06', '/img/114/286591.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2439, 'The Masque of Mandragora, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah are drawn into the Mandragora Helix, an entity which exists among the stars and which transports the TARDIS to 15th century Italy.</p>', 1, 14, 25, '1976-09-04', '/img/114/286636.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2440, 'The Masque of Mandragora, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor rushes to rescue Sarah from the Brethren of Demnos while Mandragora tries to bring them under its control.</p>', 2, 14, 25, '1976-09-11', '/img/114/286640.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2441, 'The Masque of Mandragora, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor saves Giuliano from Federico\'s men, then they try to find Sarah, unaware Hieronymous has hypnotised her to kill the Doctor.</p>', 3, 14, 25, '1976-09-18', '/img/114/286642.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2442, 'The Masque of Mandragora, Part Four', 20, '<p>With Mandragora having taken complete control of the brethren, the Doctor tries to find a way to drain off the Mandragora energy on Earth before it wipes out the guests at Giuliano\'s masque.</p>', 4, 14, 25, '1976-09-25', '/img/114/286674.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2443, 'The Hand of Fear, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah arrive in a quarry during blasting operations and when Sarah is buried under rubble, she discovers a stone hand.</p>', 5, 14, 25, '1976-10-02', '/img/114/286684.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2444, 'The Hand of Fear, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Carter attempt to gain the trust of the Nunton staff before Sarah takes the hand into the reactor.</p>', 6, 14, 25, '1976-10-09', '/img/114/286697.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2445, 'The Hand of Fear, Part Three', 20, '<p>Eldrad uses the energy from the reactor to regenerate herself and tries to force the Doctor and Sarah to take her back to Kastria.</p>', 7, 14, 25, '1976-10-16', '/img/114/286699.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2446, 'The Hand of Fear, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Sarah attempt to get Eldrad to the regeneration chamber but Rokon has left traps in their path.</p>', 8, 14, 25, '1976-10-23', '/img/114/286700.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2447, 'The Deadly Assassin, Part One', 20, '<p>A mysterious evil is at work on Gallifrey. The President of the Time Lords has been assassinated and the Doctor caught red-handed. An inexorable master plan has been set in motion. There can be no escape</p>', 9, 14, 25, '1976-10-30', '/img/114/286706.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2448, 'The Deadly Assassin, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor is arrested for the President\'s murder and struggles to avoid his immediate execution.</p>', 10, 14, 25, '1976-11-06', '/img/114/286712.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2449, 'The Deadly Assassin, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor battles the assassin inside the matrix dreamscape, while the Master tries to bring about his death in the real world.</p>', 11, 14, 25, '1976-11-13', '/img/114/286713.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2450, 'The Deadly Assassin, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor realises the Master is planning to tap into the Time Lords\' power source to extend his own life, an act that will destroy all Gallifrey.</p>', 12, 14, 25, '1976-11-20', '/img/114/286714.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2451, 'The Face of Evil, Part One', 20, '<p>On a nameless planet in the far future where invisible monsters prowl, the Doctor befriends a warrior woman named Leela, recently banished from her tribe, the Sevateem. She and everyone recognize the Doctor immediately. He is the Evil One who, in their mythology, holds their god Xoanon prisoner and must be destroyed.</p>', 13, 14, 25, '1977-01-01', '/img/114/286718.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2452, 'The Face of Evil, Part Two', 20, '<p>Despite protestations against being the Evil One, mounting evidence points to the Doctor\'s prior involvement with Leela\'s people, and an error in judgment he once made in their distant past that puts them all in immediate jeopardy.</p>', 14, 14, 25, '1977-01-08', '/img/114/286719.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2453, 'The Face of Evil, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Leela encounter the placid and mind-powerful Tesh, the complete opposite of the savage Saveteem. They recognize the Doctor, too, but to them he is Lord; however, when it becomes evident the Doctor threatens their living god, Xoanon, the Doctor becomes a marked man.</p>', 15, 14, 25, '1977-01-15', '/img/114/286741.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2454, 'The Face of Evil, Part Four', 20, '<p>As the Saveteem and Tesh finally close in for a fight to the death, the powerful but long-suffering Xoanon ignores their strife to commit its full resources toward killing the Doctor, even to the extent of destroying everyone.</p>', 16, 14, 25, '1977-01-22', '/img/114/286742.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2455, 'The Robots of Death, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS materialize aboard a sandminer, a mining ship on a desert planet run by a robot labor force headed by a fairly small but sniping human crew. As one crewman is discovered strangled to death, the Doctor and Leela arrive just in time to become the prime suspects.</p>', 17, 14, 25, '1977-01-29', '/img/114/286743.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2456, 'The Robots of Death, Part Two', 20, '<p>As the strangulations continue and the humans aren\'t sure who to blame, Leela meets up with an anomaly among the robot crew - an inquisitive, supposedly mute single-function labor robot capable of independent reasoning. Meanwhile the Doctor starts looking into the possibility that the murderer is a robot, and another crew member is targeted for death.</p>', 18, 14, 25, '1977-02-05', '/img/114/286750.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2457, 'The Robots of Death, Part Three', 20, '<p>Hearing about a man who grew up only around robots and who has threatened to start a robot revolution, and who may be aboard the sandminer under an assumed name, the Doctor takes D.84 to seek out a possible secret workshop where he would be restructuring robot programming. Meanwhile, as one crew member suffers a complete mental breakdown, reprogrammed robots are ordered to kill all remaining humans.</p>', 19, 14, 25, '1977-02-12', '/img/114/286752.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2458, 'The Robots of Death, Part Four', 20, '<p>With secrecy no longer necessary for the robot revolution, Controller Taren Capel shuts down all friendly robots and gives the remaining humans an ultimatum, or else their deaths will be slow and painful. With no conventional weaponry aboard their commercial vessel, the humans do what they can to resist while giving the Doctor time to work out a permanent solution.</p>', 20, 14, 25, '1977-02-19', '/img/114/286769.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2459, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Leela land in Victorian London, and find themselves in the middle of missing girls, mutilated bodies, and vicious Chinese gangs. The Palace theater, presenting hypnotist Li H\'sen Chang seems to be at the center of it all.</p>', 21, 14, 25, '1977-02-26', '/img/114/286775.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2460, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part Two', 20, '<p>After escaping from the vicious giant rat in the sewers, the Doctor &amp; Leela team up with Litefoot. Chang, Mr Sin and Weng-Chiang go in search of the time cabinet, while the Doctor and Jago go in search of Chiang\'s lair.</p>', 22, 14, 25, '1977-03-05', '/img/114/286776.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2461, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part Three', 20, '<p>Leela follows Chang in order to find Greel\'s hideout while the Doctor and Litefoot set about finding her.</p>', 23, 14, 25, '1977-03-12', '/img/114/286796.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2462, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part Four', 20, '<p>Having rescued Leela from the jaws of the giant vicious rat, she &amp; the Doctor dress up and attend Chang\'s show at the palace, but end up as part of the act. At home, Litefoot tries to protect the time cabinet.</p>', 24, 14, 25, '1977-03-19', '/img/114/286799.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2463, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part Five', 20, '<p>Weng-Chiang has stolen the time cabinet from Litefoot\'s house, so the Doctor and Leela go to try and stop him from using it. They find an opium-drugged Chang. Jago teams up with Litefoot for their own investigation.</p>', 25, 14, 25, '1977-03-26', '/img/114/286801.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2464, 'The Talons of Weng-Chiang, Part Six', 20, '<p>The real face of Weng-Chiang is revealed as the Doctor, Leela, Jago and Litefoot face their final battle, against both Magnus Greel and a trigger-happy Mr Sin.</p>', 26, 14, 25, '1977-04-02', '/img/114/286803.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2465, 'Horror of Fang Rock, Part One', 20, '<p>The TARDIS lands near an isolated rocky island lighthouse just after a comet strikes the nearby sea and a sudden chilling fog rolls in. Soon after, electrical problems take hold of the generator and one of the keepers dies mysteriously. Rueben, the eldest keeper, thinks it\'s the return of the legendary Beast of Fang Rock, but the Doctor suspects it\'s something worse that a legend.</p>', 1, 15, 25, '1977-09-03', '/img/114/286812.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2466, 'Horror of Fang Rock, Part Two', 20, '<p>With inexplicable electrical problems keeping the lighthouse from maintaining a steady beam, a foolhardy ship crashes against the island rocks. Four shaken and discontent survivors join the people inside where the Doctor surmises they\'re all being carefully scrutinized, a prelude to an attack.</p>', 2, 15, 25, '1977-09-10', '/img/114/286816.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2467, 'Horror of Fang Rock, Part Three', 20, '<p>A death scream is heard, yet all are accounted for. Eventually the Doctor finds a body stashed away but hours old, with rigor mortis already settling in, which means there\'s a chameleon in their midst. Completely cut off from the rest of the world and with an escalating body count, the Doctor wonders just what, exactly, he\'s locked inside the lighthouse with them all.</p>', 3, 15, 25, '1977-09-17', '/img/114/286820.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2468, 'Horror of Fang Rock, Part Four', 20, '<p>With little to fear, and its mother ship about to land and turn Earth into an alien attack base, the electrically charged Rutan scout drops its human guise and attacks openly.</p>', 4, 15, 25, '1977-09-24', '/img/114/286825.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2469, 'The Invisible Enemy, Part One', 20, '<p>\"Contact has been made!\" A relief crew en route to Titan in 5000 AD unwarily pick up hitchhikers that change them. Shortly thereafter the Doctor, passing through the same point in space, is hitchhiked as well, but not Leela - a reject who must die.</p>', 5, 15, 25, '1977-10-01', '/img/114/287025.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2470, 'The Invisible Enemy, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor draws into himself, fighting the voice in his own head that\'s trying to take over his intelligence.</p>', 6, 15, 25, '1977-10-08', '/img/114/287029.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2471, 'The Invisible Enemy, Part Three', 20, '<p>The medical center mounts a defense against alien forces trying to take the comatose Doctor while clones of Leela and the Doctor go microscopic so they can hunt down the intelligent infection that\'s in his head.</p>', 7, 15, 25, '1977-10-15', '/img/114/287032.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2472, 'The Invisible Enemy, Part Four', 20, '<p>In trying to retrieve the clones from inside the Doctor, the alien virus is brought from the microbial world into the macro-world, and it\'s ready to spawn.</p>', 8, 15, 25, '1977-10-22', '/img/114/287034.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2473, 'Image of the Fendahl, Part One', 20, '<p>Archeologists near a reputedly haunted woods use a time scanner to explore the history of a sinister 12 million year old skull, creating a hole in time that attracts the Doctor\'s attention.</p>', 9, 15, 25, '1977-10-29', '/img/82/205159.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2474, 'Image of the Fendahl, Part Two', 20, '<p>Every time the archaeologists explore the ancient skull, something deadly hunts and haunts the wood while one of the researchers is particularly affected.</p>', 10, 15, 25, '1977-11-05', '/img/82/205177.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2475, 'Image of the Fendahl, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor endeavors to prevent the re-existence of a Fendahl, a group entity that feeds on life itself and thought only to exist in Time Lord mythology, but a witches\' coven, seeking power, intervenes.</p>', 11, 15, 25, '1977-11-12', '/img/82/205189.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2476, 'Image of the Fendahl, Part Four', 20, '<p>With one of the archaeologists transformed and a massive implosion threatening, the Fendahl and its Fendahleen components start coming into existence while the Doctor, Leela and the Tylers do what they can to stop it.</p>', 12, 15, 25, '1977-11-19', '/img/82/205196.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2477, 'The Sun Makers, Part One', 20, '<p>The Tardis lands on Pluto in the far future. Instead of being a lifeless rock, there\'s scented air, massive buildings, six suns, a human population subjugated by crippling taxes from a government called \"The Company,\" and a man about to commit suicide.</p>', 13, 15, 25, '1977-11-26', '/img/114/287051.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2478, 'The Sun Makers, Part Two', 20, '<p>Captured by the authorities, the Doctor finds himself restrained in a Correction Centre where he\'s to be prepped for painful shock treatments, making him unable to return within a given time frame to the underground rebels holding Leela, who are prepared to kill her as promised.</p>', 14, 15, 25, '1977-12-03', '/img/115/287932.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2479, 'The Sun Makers, Part Three', 20, '<p>The merciless Collector, who runs The Company, issues a bounty on the Doctor for his capture, while an already captured Leela is sentenced to public execution, via a steamer, for crimes against the company.</p>', 15, 15, 25, '1977-12-10', '/img/115/287933.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2480, 'The Sun Makers, Part Four', 20, '<p>Attempting to start a successful revolution, the Doctor uses Pluto\'s Public Address System to announce successful revolution, all the while trying to determine the Collector\'s true species and why he, or it, seems set on taxing the life out of humans.</p>', 16, 15, 25, '1977-12-17', '/img/115/287934.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2481, 'Underworld, Part One', 20, '<p>Materializing at the edge of the cosmos, the frontier of creation, The Doctor, Leela &amp; K-9 encounter four ancient space travelers from Minyos, the first race ever contacted by the Time Lords. All but extinct due to their Time Lords encounter, the Minyans (rejuvenated 1000 times each) have been embarked on a long 100,000 year old quest, searching the universe for the lost race bank of their species to take to a new home world. But their equally old ship is finally failing, succumbing to the gravitational pull of a newly forming sun and taking the Doctor and his party with it.</p>', 17, 15, 25, '1978-01-07', '/img/115/287935.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2482, 'Underworld, Part Two', 20, '<p>Crashing inside a newly formed planet, the Doctor and others find it inhabited by a slave labor mining society, where rocks are harvested for their radioactive energy and human life has little value. With a population controlled by deliberate cave-ins, poison gas, and periodic sacrifices to an Oracle, the miners, called Trogs, are also descendants from Minyos, and who desperately desire freedom.</p>', 18, 15, 25, '1978-01-14', '/img/115/287936.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2483, 'Underworld, Part Three', 20, '<p>Capturing the Doctor and Leela, the citadel guards are quite pleased to have more subjects for their public executions, but it only fires up a Trog revolt instead.</p>', 19, 15, 25, '1978-01-21', '/img/115/287937.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2484, 'Underworld, Part Four', 20, '<p>With the Trog revolt close to success, the Oracle grants the Minyos travelers what they seek (the long lost race bank) in hopes they\'ll depart peacefully and straight away, but the Doctor suspects it\'s not all going to be as amicable as that. And what to do about the Trogs?</p>', 20, 15, 25, '1978-01-28', '/img/115/287938.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2485, 'The Invasion of Time, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor returns to Gallifrey to become the President of the High Council of Time Lords. But Leela realizes that the Doctor is acting out of character.</p>', 21, 15, 25, '1978-02-04', '/img/115/287954.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2486, 'The Invasion of Time, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor orders Leela exiled from the Capitol, then orders K9 to sabotage Gallifrey\'s defences.</p>', 22, 15, 25, '1978-02-11', '/img/115/287956.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2487, 'The Invasion of Time, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor allows the Vardans to occupy Gallifrey while Leela and Rodan head out into the wasteland to search for help.</p>', 23, 15, 25, '1978-02-18', '/img/115/287957.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2488, 'The Invasion of Time, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor convinces Andred to trust him as he works to expel the Vardans, while Leela gathers the Outsiders for an attack on the Capitol.</p>', 24, 15, 25, '1978-02-25', '/img/115/287958.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2489, 'The Invasion of Time, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends flee from the Sontarans and the Doctor tries to convince Borusa to abandon his sacred office in order to help defeat them.</p>', 25, 15, 25, '1978-03-04', '/img/115/287969.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2490, 'The Invasion of Time, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and his friends take refuge in the TARDIS but find themselves pursued by Stor and Kelner.</p>', 26, 15, 25, '1978-03-11', '/img/115/287970.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2491, 'The Ribos Operation, Part One', 20, '<p>The Guardian of Time gives the Doctor a difficult task,and a new assistant. Together they must search for the six segments of the Key to Time, to prevent the Universe from being plunged into eternal chaos. On their mission, the Doctor and Romana travel to the planet Ribos where the first segment of the key is protected by the monstrous Shrivenzale.</p>', 1, 16, 25, '1978-09-02', '/img/115/287971.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2492, 'The Ribos Operation, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Romana investigate Garron\'s activities but this results in the Graff believing they are working together.</p>', 2, 16, 25, '1978-09-09', '/img/115/287974.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2493, 'The Ribos Operation, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Graff takes the Doctor, Romana and Garron prisoner and then sets about trying to track down Unstoffe and the jethryk.</p>', 3, 16, 25, '1978-09-16', '/img/115/288395.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2494, 'The Ribos Operation, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor returns to the city to keep an eye on the Graff, leaving Romana, K9 and Garron to search for Unstoffe and the first segment. However, Garron double crosses them and steals the tracer.</p>', 4, 16, 25, '1978-09-23', '/img/115/288396.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2495, 'The Pirate Planet, Part One', 20, '<p>In seeking the second segment of the Key to Time, the TARDIS heads for an icy world but lands on a populated planet that shouldn\'t be there.</p>', 5, 16, 25, '1978-09-30', '/img/115/288401.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2496, 'The Pirate Planet, Part Two', 20, '<p>After the Mentiads knock the Doctor out, he discovers that Romana has been taken to the planets bridge. He then travels to the bridge to help her and ends up being forced to help repair the engines.</p>', 6, 16, 25, '1978-10-07', '/img/141/353443.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2497, 'The Pirate Planet, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor takes Romana down to investigate the planets mines and gets unexpected help when the Captains guards show up to confront them.</p>', 7, 16, 25, '1978-10-14', '/img/141/353447.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2498, 'The Pirate Planet, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Mentiads with the help of the Doctor work to foil Queen Xanxia\'s plan to regain a body and destroy Earth in the process.</p>', 8, 16, 25, '1978-10-21', '/img/141/353452.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2499, 'The Stones of Blood, Part One', 20, '<p>In their search for the 3rd segment of the key to time, the Doctor and Romana land on Earth at a Stonehenge type site where worshipers are engaged in their practice and people are being killed by unknown causes. While en route the Doctor and Romana hear a strange voice that says \'Beware the Black Guardian\".</p>', 9, 16, 25, '1978-10-28', '/img/142/356419.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2500, 'The Stones of Blood, Part Two', 20, '<p>Romana ends up hanging on the side of a cliff while the Doctor is captured by Druid pagan worshipers. The Doctor and the Professor then go on a search for Romana after finding her shoes.</p>', 10, 16, 25, '1978-11-04', '/img/142/356418.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2501, 'The Stones of Blood, Part Three', 20, '<p>The Doctor transfers to Hyperspace to save Romana from her imprisonment and has a run in with the Megara Justice machines during his search.</p>', 11, 16, 25, '1978-11-11', '/img/142/356420.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2502, 'The Stones of Blood, Part Four', 20, '<p>The Doctor convinces the Megara to give Vivien Fay a truth test while playing for time so Romana can get back to Earth and find evidence against Vivien.</p>', 12, 16, 25, '1978-11-18', '/img/142/356424.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2503, 'The Androids of Tara, Part One', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Romana are now searching for the 3rd segment of the Key to Time. Landing on the world of Tara, the Doctor decides to send Romana off in search of the 3rd segment while he takes a break and does some fishing.</p>', 13, 16, 25, '1978-11-25', '/img/143/359165.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2504, 'The Androids of Tara, Part Two', 20, '<p>Romana is being held prisoner by Count Grendal, the Prince and his men along with the Doctor are drugged when they toast to the king after the Doctor has fixed the Prince\'s android. He is then accused of being involved in the Princes disappearance. They then have to figure out a plan to still get the android crowned as the Prince has vanished while the men were unconscious.</p>', 14, 16, 25, '1978-12-02', '/img/143/359167.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2505, 'The Androids of Tara, Part Three', 20, '<p>The confirmation of the King has been put on hold, and the Doctor works on repairing the android of the future king in time. Count Grendal meanwhile, having had his plans interrupted works to stop the confirmation so he can become king in the Princes place.</p>', 15, 16, 25, '1978-12-09', '/img/143/359182.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2506, 'The Androids of Tara, Part Four', 20, '<p>After the Doctor escapes Grendel\'s trap, plans are made to rescue both the Prince and Strella. Count Grendel continues to finalize his plan to take over the kingship.</p>', 16, 16, 25, '1978-12-16', '/img/143/359183.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2507, 'The Power of Kroll, Part One', 20, '', 17, 16, 25, '1978-12-23', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2508, 'The Power of Kroll, Part Two', 20, '', 18, 16, 25, '1978-12-30', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2509, 'The Power of Kroll, Part Three', 20, '', 19, 16, 25, '1979-01-06', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2510, 'The Power of Kroll, Part Four', 20, '', 20, 16, 25, '1979-01-13', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2511, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part One', 20, '<p>In their search for the final segment of the \'Key To Time\', the Doctor and Romana land the TARDIS on the world of Atrios who is at war with it\'s neighboring planet Zeos. Upon avoiding a missile attack right before landing, the Doctor and Time Lady Romana are then mistaken for spys from Zeos by the Marshall.</p>', 21, 16, 25, '1979-01-20', '/img/146/367448.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2512, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Two', 20, '<p>When the Doctor and Romana work to escape they Marshal, they not only discover that their TARDIS has been buried underneath a pile of rubble from a recent Zeos attack, but also they discover someone who may be trapped and kidnapped by a unknown source.</p>', 22, 16, 25, '1979-01-27', '/img/147/367674.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2513, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Three', 20, '<p>While faithful K-9 awaits the return of the Doctor and those with him, he is taken prisoner by The Shadow. With The Marshal determined to attack Zeos, the Doctor has to put a halt to his plan in order to save Atrios and billions of lives. </p>', 23, 16, 25, '1979-02-03', '/img/147/367677.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2514, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Four', 20, '<p>K-9 communicates with the leader of the Zeos world and the Doctor attempts to keep the leader from completing it\'s plan. The Doctor and companions discover the unknown world that is between Atrios and Zeos.</p>', 24, 16, 25, '1979-02-10', '/img/147/367680.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2515, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Five', 20, '<p>The Doctor with Drax\'s help, escape from their prison and work to stop The Shadows plan. The Shadow uses Astra to further the Black Guardians plot to obtain the Key to Time.</p>', 25, 16, 25, '1979-02-17', '/img/147/367683.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2516, 'The Armageddon Factor, Part Six', 20, '<p>The Doctor and Romana prevent the Marshal from concluding his plan and discover what the last segment of the Key to Time actually is. They then encounter both the Black Guardian and The White Guardian in their effort to conclude the mission given to them by the White Guardian.</p>', 26, 16, 25, '1979-02-24', '/img/147/367684.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2517, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part One', 20, '<p>Romana experiments with regeneration while the Doctor prepares to land on a world that is experiencing periodic earthquakes and seems strangely familiar to him.</p>', 1, 17, 25, '1979-09-01', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2518, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part Two', 20, '<p>After discovering that the world they are on is the Dalek\'s home planet of Skaro, the Doctor starts to question the reason for the Movellans being there. Meanwhile, Romana is captured by the Daleks.</p>', 2, 17, 25, '1979-09-08', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2519, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part Three', 20, '', 3, 17, 25, '1979-09-15', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2520, 'Destiny of the Daleks, Part Four', 20, '', 4, 17, 25, '1979-09-22', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2521, 'City of Death, Part One', 20, '<p>While the Doctor is exploring and showing the sights of Paris to Romana, they encounter what seems to be a blip in time. He then takes Romana to see the Mona Lisa and discovers a woman with Jewlery that seems out of place.</p>', 5, 17, 25, '1979-09-29', '/img/158/396646.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2522, 'City of Death, Part Two', 20, '<p>The Doctor, Romana and Duggan are taken prisoner by the Count and questioned about why the Doctor was so interested in the Countess\'s bracelet.</p>', 6, 17, 25, '1979-10-06', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2523, 'City of Death, Part Three', 20, '', 7, 17, 25, '1979-10-13', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2524, 'City of Death, Part Four', 20, '', 8, 17, 25, '1979-10-20', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2525, 'The Creature from the Pit, Part One', 20, '', 9, 17, 25, '1979-10-27', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2526, 'The Creature from the Pit, Part Two', 20, '', 10, 17, 25, '1979-11-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2527, 'The Creature from the Pit, Part Three', 20, '', 11, 17, 25, '1979-11-10', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
(2528, 'The Creature from the Pit, Part Four', 20, '', 12, 17, 25, '1979-11-17', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:09', '2019-12-19 02:15:09'),
