(3606, 'Dux bellorum', 32, '<p>Arthurus is appointed war leader, but he doesn\'t believe he deserves the title.</p>', 5, 6, 7, '2009-10-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3607, 'Nuptiæ', 32, '<p>King Léodagan of Carmélide refuses to unite his kingdom with the future King Arthur, unless he marries his daughter.</p>', 6, 6, 7, '2009-10-24', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3608, 'Arturus rex', 32, '<p>Arthurus land in Brittany to become King. He has to remove Excalibur from the rock and hire knights. On his way he meets Perceval and Karadoc.</p>', 7, 6, 7, '2009-10-31', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3609, 'Lacrimosa', 32, '<p>King Arthur marries Guenièvre as a political move. He also has a plan to kick the Romans out of Brittany.</p>', 8, 6, 7, '2009-10-31', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3610, 'Dies iræ', 32, '<p>King Arthur has finished to tell his full story. People come to pay him their respects, but he is still alive. Very weak, he gives away his full powers, but things don\'t go as expected, and King Arthur has to take a surprising decision.</p>', 9, 6, 7, '2009-10-31', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3611, 'Heat', 32, '<p>Stuck in the forest during a battle, King Arthur and Léodagan listen with despair to Perceval\'s crazy ideas to avoid the enemies.</p>', 1, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3612, 'Les tartes aux myrtilles', 32, '<p>Arthur, Guinevere and Leodagan are forced to eat the inedible blueberry pie cooked by Dame Séli.</p>', 2, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3613, 'La table de Breccan', 32, '<p>The round table ordered by King Arthur has arrived.</p>', 3, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3614, 'Le Chevalier mystère', 32, '<p>King Arthur and The Knights of the Round Table are discussing the fate of a mysterious knight called Provençal le Gaulois, or is it Perceval?</p>', 4, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3615, 'Le fléau de Dieu', 32, '<p>King Arthur, Léodagan and Bohort negotiate with Attila the Hun in the throne room, who demands all the gold of Kaamelott.</p>', 5, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3616, 'Le Garde du corps', 32, '<p>King Arthur is close to sign a peace treaty and is assigned a new bodyguard, who follows him everywhere, even when he is in bed with his mistresses.</p>', 6, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3617, 'Des nouvelles du monde', 32, '<p>A barb invited to dinner sings odes far from accurate.</p>', 7, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3618, 'Codes et Stratégies', 32, '<p>King Arthur and his knights are sending signals to their troops from a hill nearby, but nobody is following his orders.</p>', 8, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3619, 'Le Maître d\'armes', 32, '<p>King Arthur is training with his fencing master who insults him copiously. The only way for him to fight his King, and urges him to call him names too. At first reluctant, the King seems to enjoy it very much, to the despair of his fencing master.</p>', 9, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3620, 'Le négociateur', 32, '<p>Kaamelott is under attack and Bohort has made an unacceptable deal with the enemy. King Arthur refuses it and sends his troops to the fight.</p>', 10, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3621, 'Dîner dansant', 32, '<p>A family diner at Kaamelott, where everyone wants to be elsewhere, turn to another pitched battle.</p>', 11, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3622, 'Le Sixième Sens', 32, '<p>King Arthur has Summoned Perceval and Karadoc at the Round Table as the lady of the lake would like to reveal Perceval\'s fate. King Arthur struggles to explain why he is the only one able to see her.</p>', 12, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3623, 'Arthur et la Question', 32, '<p>Léodagan has failed to get a thief to talk. He seeks help from Venec who sells a vast array of instruments of torture.</p>', 13, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3624, 'Monogame', 32, '<p>King Arthur refuses to outlaw polygamy.</p>', 14, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3625, 'Les Défis de Merlin', 32, '<p>A foreign wizard defies Merlin over the ownership of a nearby land.</p>', 15, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3626, 'Les Banquets des chefs', 32, '<p>Everyone is helping with the upcoming festivities in grand style while Camelot gets ready to receive the chieftains.</p>', 16, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3627, 'Le Signe', 32, '<p>A dead crow is found in front of the King\'s door. He asks Merlin if it\'s a bad sign.</p>', 17, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3628, 'En forme de Graal', 32, '<p>The knights of the Round Table enter a heated debate about the true shape of the Graal.</p>', 18, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3629, 'Le Repos du guerrier', 32, '<p>The King is subject to criticism for having his mood depending on whether he had spent his night with the Queen or his mistresses.</p>', 19, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3630, 'La Dent de requin', 32, '<p>During a battle Merlin needs a shark tooth for his magic spell. Perceval and Karadoc are sent back to Camelot to get one. Meanwhile Merlin has found a possible replacement, but the spell only made the enemy laughing out loud.</p>', 20, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
(3631, 'La Taxe militaire', 32, '<p>A presumed dead nobleman arrives at Camelot to complain that he doesn\'t benefit of the tax exemptions accorded to nobles.</p>', 21, 1, 7, '2005-01-03', NULL, '2019-12-19 02:15:13', '2019-12-19 02:15:13'),
