(3711, 'Tape 1, Side A', 33, '<p>As the school mourns the death of Hannah Baker, her friend Clay receives a box of tapes with messages she recorded before she committed suicide.</p>', 1, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/104/262310.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3712, 'Tape 1, Side B', 33, '<p>Hannah makes friends with Jessica and Alex, two other new students. Justin doesn\'t show up at school, and Hannah\'s mother finds something troubling.</p>', 2, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/262514.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3713, 'Tape 2, Side A', 33, '<p>Jealousy and gossip take a toll on Hannah\'s relationships. As Alex struggles with feelings of regret, the guys pressure Clay into getting drunk.</p>', 3, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/262867.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3714, 'Tape 2, Side B', 33, '<p>Hannah thinks someone is stalking her and sets a trap. Hannah\'s mother confronts the principal, and Clay strikes back at someone who wronged Hannah.</p>', 4, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/262965.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3715, 'Tape 3, Side A', 33, '<p>Hannah and Clay connect at the school dance, but a crass rumor ruins the mood. Clay takes Courtney to visit Hannah\'s grave.</p>', 5, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/263240.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3716, 'Tape 3, Side B', 33, '<p>Hannah\'s date on Valentine\'s Day doesn\'t go as planned. Alex gets in a big fight at school and has to face the honor board.</p>', 6, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/263622.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3717, 'Tape 4, Side A', 33, '<p>Another student sabotages Hannah during a class project. Clay\'s nightmares about Hannah spill over into the daytime.</p>', 7, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/263650.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3718, 'Tape 4, Side B', 33, '<p>Inspired by a friend\'s poetry reading, Hannah pours her heart out. Tony confides in Clay about the night of Hannah\'s death.</p>', 8, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/263983.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3719, 'Tape 5, Side A', 33, '<p>Hannah witnesses a traumatic event at a summertime party. Clay tries to reason with Justin, and Marcus warns him that the worst is yet to come.</p>', 9, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/264428.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3720, 'Tape 5, Side B', 33, '<p>A distraught Hannah gets a ride home from the party. Jessica\'s behavior grows increasingly erratic, and Clay learns the truth behind a tragedy.</p>', 10, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/264450.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3721, 'Tape 6, Side A', 33, '<p>Clay and Hannah grow closer. While Clay spends a heartbreaking night listening to his tape with Tony, tensions boil over at Bryce\'s house.</p>', 11, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/264471.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3722, 'Tape 6, Side B', 33, '<p>Hannah winds up at a party after an argument with her parents. The students are served with subpoenas, and Justin wrestles with conflicting loyalties.</p>', 12, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/264495.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3723, 'Tape 7, Side A', 33, '<p>Hannah seeks help from Mr. Porter, the school counselor. Clay plays the new tape for Tony and weighs what to do next.</p>', 13, 1, 60, '2017-03-31', '/img/105/264516.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3724, 'The First Polaroid', 33, '<p>Five months after Hannah\'s death, the case against Liberty goes to trial, with Tyler as the first witness. Clay finds a troubling photo in his locker.</p>', 1, 2, 60, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397372.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3725, 'Two Girls Kissing', 33, '<p>Courtney makes a brave decision. Clay\'s memories of Hannah drive a wedge between him and Skye. Someone trashes the yearbook office.</p>', 2, 2, 60, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397371.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3726, 'The Drunk Slut', 33, '<p>Worried about threats against them, Alex and Clay urge Jessica to testify about Bryce. Clay enlists Tony\'s help to find a potential witness.</p>', 3, 2, 57, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397370.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3727, 'The Second Polaroid', 33, '<p>Clay hides a secret from his parents. Concerned about his reputation, Marcus lies in court. Jessica and Alex skip school together.</p>', 4, 2, 57, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397369.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3728, 'The Chalk Machine', 33, '<p>Tyler and Cyrus embrace their outsider status. Alex fights to recover his lost memories. Ryan and Mrs. Baker look to Hannah\'s poems for clues.</p>', 5, 2, 57, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397368.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3729, 'The Smile at the End of the Dock', 33, '<p>Clay tries to figure out where the Polaroids were taken. Justin shows up at school. Zach\'s revelation about Hannah takes everyone by surprise.</p>', 6, 2, 58, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397367.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3730, 'The Third Polaroid', 33, '<p>Alex blows up at Bryce. Someone blackmails Marcus. Clay testifies about a night he and Hannah spent together. Jessica experiences a flashback.</p>', 7, 2, 56, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397366.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3731, 'The Little Girl', 33, '<p>When Hannah\'s parents come under scrutiny, Jessica reaches out to Mrs. Baker. Justin struggles to stay clean. Clay reconnects with Skye.</p>', 8, 2, 57, '2018-05-18', '/img/156/390164.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3732, 'The Missing Page', 33, '<p>Tyler goes out with Cyrus\'s sister. Chloe confronts Bryce about the tapes. Jess wonders if she\'s ready to date again. Mr. Porter wrestles with regret.</p>', 9, 2, 57, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397365.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3733, 'Smile, Bitches!', 33, '<p>Tony opens up about his past. Sheri devises a plan to get into the clubhouse. Mr. Porter tries to help Justin. Zach and Bryce butt heads.</p>', 10, 2, 55, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397364.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3734, 'Bryce and Chloe', 33, '<p>Chaos erupts at school in the aftermath of Bryce\'s testimony. Jessica tells Chloe about the clubhouse. Alex\'s memories come rushing back.</p>', 11, 2, 58, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397376.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3735, 'The Box of Polaroids', 33, '<p>Threats against Clay and the others escalate. Tyler faces disciplinary action. Justin testifies about Bryce, putting his own future at risk.</p>', 12, 2, 56, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397375.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3736, 'Bye', 33, '<p>One month later, Hannah\'s loved ones celebrate her life and find comfort in each other. Meanwhile, a brutal assault pushes one student over the edge.</p>', 13, 2, 70, '2018-05-18', '/img/158/397373.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3737, 'Yeah. I\'m the New Girl', 33, '<p>The cops question Clay about Bryce\'s disappearance. Clay remembers the aftermath of Spring Fling, when he raced to cover Tyler\'s tracks and met Ani.</p>', 1, 3, 56, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521961.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3738, 'If You\'re Breathing, You\'re a Liar', 33, '<p>After learning about Chloe\'s pregnancy, Clay and Ani pay her a visit. Chloe recalls how she leaned on Zach for support -- and that Bryce never knew.</p>', 2, 3, 57, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521962.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3739, 'The Good Person Is Indistinguishable from the Bad', 33, '<p>As the police investigation sets the school on edge, Ani remembers that Jessica confronted Bryce. Growing suspicious of Jess, Ani and Clay follow her.</p>', 3, 3, 60, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521963.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3740, 'Angry, Young and Man', 33, '<p>After Tyler admits he still has a gun, the group keeps tabs on him at school. But their worry deepens when they learn he had a motive to kill Bryce.</p>', 4, 3, 58, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521964.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3741, 'Nobody\'s Clean', 33, '<p>The police search the school after finding steroids in Bryce\'s car. Alex remembers how Bryce supported Alex after Jessica dumped him.</p>', 5, 3, 60, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521965.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3742, 'You Can Tell the Heart of a Man by How He Grieves', 33, '<p>The police bring in Tony for questioning. At Bryce\'s funeral, Ani uncovers two damning secrets.</p>', 6, 3, 57, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521966.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3743, 'There Are a Number of Problems with Clay Jensen', 33, '<p>The police interrogate Justin and Clay about the night Clay pulled a gun on Bryce. Clay discovers that Ani and Bryce\'s bond ran deeper than he realized.</p>', 7, 3, 49, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521967.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3744, 'In High School, Even on a Good Day, It\'s Hard to Tell Who\'s on Your Side', 33, '<p>Mr. Porter interviews students about Clay, who pleads his innocence to Mrs. Walker. Learning Porter counseled Bryce, Clay and Ani question his motives.</p>', 8, 3, 51, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521968.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3745, 'Always Waiting for the Next Bad News', 33, '<p>The cops name Clay as a person of interest in the murder. Ani catches Justin in a lie after learning Bryce bailed him out of a dangerous situation.</p>', 9, 3, 55, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521969.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3746, 'The World Closing In', 33, '<p>Hannah\'s mother returns to town. Urging Clay to protect himself, she reveals that there was more to Tony and Bryce\'s relationship than Clay knew.</p>', 10, 3, 54, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521970.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3747, 'There Are a Few Things I Haven\'t Told You', 33, '<p>As the cops close in on Clay -- their main suspect -- violent confrontations at the homecoming game expose that everyone had a reason to kill Bryce.</p>', 11, 3, 54, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521971.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3748, 'And Then the Hurricane Hit', 33, '<p>The pressure of Clay\'s arrest leads his friends to make risky decisions, and the full story of the brawl that erupted at homecoming emerges.</p>', 12, 3, 59, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521972.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3749, 'Let the Dead Bury the Dead', 33, '<p>Clay is released on bail, Ani puts a plan to exonerate him into action, and the truth about Bryce\'s murder finally comes to light.</p>', 13, 3, 72, '2019-08-23', '/img/208/521973.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3750, 'The Vulcan Hello', 34, '<p>While patrolling Federation space, the U.S.S. Shenzhou encounters an object of unknown origin, putting First Officer Michael Burnham to her greatest test yet.</p>', 1, 1, 60, '2017-09-24', '/img/128/322025.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3751, 'Battle at the Binary Stars', 34, '<p>Face to face with Klingon vessels, the U.S.S. Shenzhou prepares for the possibility of war if negotiations fail. Amidst the turmoil, Burnham looks back to her Vulcan upbringing for guidance.</p>', 2, 1, 60, '2017-09-24', '/img/128/322287.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3752, 'Context Is for Kings', 34, '<p>Burnham finds herself aboard the U.S.S. Discovery where she quickly realizes things are not as they seem, including the mysterious Captain Gabriel Lorca.</p>', 3, 1, 60, '2017-10-01', '/img/129/324412.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3753, 'The Butcher\'s Knife Cares Not for the Lamb\'s Cry', 34, '<p>With tensions and stakes high as Starfleet continues in their efforts to end the war with Klingons, Burnham begins to settle in to her new position aboard the U.S.S. Discovery.</p>', 4, 1, 60, '2017-10-08', '/img/130/326569.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3754, 'Choose Your Pain', 34, '<p>While on a mission, Lorca unexpectedly finds himself in the company of prisoner of war, Starfleet Lieutenant Ash Tyler and notorious intergalactic criminal, Harry Mudd. Burnham voices her concerns about the repercussions of the spore drive jumps on \"Ripper\".</p>', 5, 1, 60, '2017-10-15', '/img/131/328978.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3755, 'Lethe', 34, '<p>The U.S.S. Discovery crew is intrigued by new addition, Lt. Ash Tyler. Sarek seeks Burnham\'s help, rekindling memories from her past. Admiral Cornwell questions Lorca\'s tactics.</p>', 6, 1, 60, '2017-10-22', '/img/132/330735.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3756, 'Magic to Make the Sanest Man Go Mad', 34, '<p>As the U.S.S. Discovery crew attempts to let loose at a party, an unwelcome visitor comes aboard bringing about a problematic and twisted sequence of events.</p>', 7, 1, 60, '2017-10-29', '/img/133/332957.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3757, 'Si Vis Pacem, Para Bellum', 34, '<p>The U.S.S. Discovery is tasked with a high priority mission to planet Pahvo and learn the science behind the Klingons\' cloaking technology.</p>', 8, 1, 60, '2017-11-05', '/img/133/332925.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3758, 'Into the Forest I Go', 34, '<p>Bypassing Starfleet\'s orders, Lorca uses the U.S.S. Discovery crew\'s ultimate asset, the ship itself, in an effort to end the war with the Klingons once and for all.</p>', 9, 1, 60, '2017-11-12', '/img/134/335131.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3759, 'Despite Yourself', 34, '<p>While in unfamiliar territory, the U.S.S. Discovery crew is forced to get creative in their next efforts to survive opposing and unprecedented forces and return home.</p>', 10, 1, 60, '2018-01-07', '/img/135/337690.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3760, 'The Wolf Inside', 34, '<p>The crew continues their guise; Burnham goes on a mission in hopes of helping the U.S.S. Discovery return home; Tilly works to restore Stamets</p>', 11, 1, 60, '2018-01-14', '/img/142/356316.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3761, 'Vaulting Ambition', 34, '<p>Burnham heads to the ISS Charon with a special \"gift\" for the Emperor. With the help of an unexpected source, Stamets gains clarity while trapped inside the mycelial network. Saru asks for L\'Rell\'s help.</p>', 12, 1, 60, '2018-01-21', '/img/142/356125.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3762, 'What\'s Past Is Prologue', 34, '<p>Lorca plans to move forward with a coup against the Emperor, propelling Burnham to make a quick decision to save not only herself, but the U.S.S. Discovery.</p>', 13, 1, 60, '2018-01-28', '/img/143/358013.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3763, 'The War Without, the War Within', 34, '<p>Back on the USS Discovery, Michael Burnham and the crew are faced with the harsh reality of the war during their absence. In order to move forward, Starfleet must use unconventional tactics and sources to take their next action against the Klingons.</p>', 14, 1, 60, '2018-02-04', '/img/145/362809.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3764, 'Will You Take My Hand?', 34, '<p>With Georgiou at the helm of the plan to end the Klingon war once and for all, the U.S.S. Discovery crew struggles to fathom and tolerate her hostile tactics. Memories of past hardships are rekindled within Burnham.</p>', 15, 1, 60, '2018-02-11', '/img/146/365064.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3765, 'Brother', 34, '<p>After answering a distress signal from the U.S.S. Enterprise, the U.S.S. Discovery welcomes aboard Captain Christopher Pike and begins a new mission to investigate the meaning behind seven mysterious red signals. Michael Burnham grapples with her past growing up on Vulcan with her foster parents and brother Spock.</p>', 1, 2, 60, '2019-01-17', '/img/180/450978.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3766, 'New Eden', 34, '<p>A new signal appears, prompting Stamets\' emotional return to the mycelial network and leading Burnham, Pike and Owosekun to a pre-warp planet, where they face a complex ethical dilemma. Tilly\'s overeagerness lands her in trouble but when the planet – and Discovery\'s landing party – are threatened, her curiosity may be the one thing that can save them.</p>', 2, 2, 60, '2019-01-24', '/img/181/453436.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3767, 'Point of Light', 34, '<p>A surprise visitor to the U.S.S. Discovery brings shocking news about Spock and dredges up past regrets for Burnham. Following the asteroid incident, Tilly struggles to keep a grip on her reality. L\'Rell\'s authority on Qo\'noS is threatened.</p>', 3, 2, 60, '2019-01-31', '/img/182/455369.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3768, 'An Obol for Charon', 34, '<p>A mysterious sphere threatens the U.S.S. Discovery even as May, in her original form, implements a plan that puts Tilly\'s life in danger. Saru and Burnham\'s bond grows when Saru is forced to acknowledge a deeply unsettling Kelpien truth. Pike receives new intel on Spock from a loyal friend.</p>', 4, 2, 60, '2019-02-07', '/img/182/455535.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3769, 'Saints of Imperfection', 34, '<p>Burnham and the crew navigate a dangerous alien landscape in a race against time to save Tilly\'s life, but Stamets is not at all prepared for what they find in the process. Section 31 is assigned to help track down Spock, much to Pike\'s dismay.</p>', 5, 2, 60, '2019-02-14', '/img/184/460236.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3770, 'The Sounds of Thunder', 34, '<p>When a new signal appears over Saru\'s home planet, Burnham, Saru and the crew embark on a perilous mission that puts Saru in danger and raises questions about the Red Angel\'s intentions. Hugh struggles to come to terms with his new reality.</p>', 6, 2, 60, '2019-02-21', '/img/184/460237.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3771, 'Light and Shadows', 34, '<p>Burnham goes to Vulcan in search of Spock, where she unearths surprising family secrets. In researching what is left of the Red Angel\'s signal over Kaminar, Pike and Tyler end up in battle with time itself. Georgiou has a few tricks up her sleeve for Leland and Section 31.</p>', 7, 2, 60, '2019-02-28', '/img/184/462433.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3772, 'If Memory Serves', 34, '<p>Spock and Burnham head to Talos IV, where the process of healing Spock forces the siblings to confront their troubled past. Stamets desperately tries to reconnect with an increasingly disconnected Hugh, while Tyler struggles to shed the crew\'s suspicions of him due to his past as Voq.</p>', 8, 2, 60, '2019-03-07', '/img/186/465259.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3773, 'Project Daedalus', 34, '<p>When the Discovery crew infiltrates Section 31\'s headquarters, suspicions arise that the crew may have a traitor in their midst. Burnham tries to help Spock but her efforts don\'t go as planned.</p>', 9, 2, 60, '2019-03-14', '/img/187/467861.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3774, 'The Red Angel', 34, '<p>Burnham is stunned when she learns her ties to Section 31 run deeper than she ever fathomed. Armed with the identity of the Red Angel, the U.S.S. Discovery goes to work on its most critical mission to date.</p>', 10, 2, 60, '2019-03-21', '/img/189/472660.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3775, 'Perpetual Infinity', 34, '<p>Burnham receives the reunion she\'s been longing for, but it doesn\'t go quite as she imagined. Georgiou and Tyler sense a disturbing change in Leland.</p>', 11, 2, 60, '2019-03-28', '/img/189/473157.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3776, 'Through the Valley of Shadows', 34, '<p>A fourth signal leads the U.S.S. Discovery to an insular world, where Pike is forced to make a life-changing choice. Burnham and Spock investigate a Section 31 ship gone rogue, leading to a discovery with catastrophic consequences.</p>', 12, 2, 60, '2019-04-04', '/img/189/474712.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3777, 'Such Sweet Sorrow', 34, '<p>When the U.S.S. Discovery\'s crucial mission does not go according to plan, Burnham realizes what must ultimately be done. The crew prepares for the battle of a lifetime as Leland\'s Control ships get closer.</p>', 13, 2, 60, '2019-04-11', '/img/190/476521.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3778, 'Such Sweet Sorrow, Part 2', 34, '<p>The U.S.S. Discovery battles against Control in a fight not only for their lives but for the future, with a little help from some unexpected friends. Spock and Burnham discern vital new connections between the red signals while Burnham faces one of life\'s harshest truths: the right decisions are often the hardest to make.</p>', 14, 2, 60, '2019-04-18', '/img/192/481140.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3779, 'Lyra\'s Jordan', 35, '<p>Orphan Lyra Belacqua\'s world is turned upside-down by her long-absent uncle\'s return from the north, while the glamorous Mrs Coulter visits Jordan College with a proposition.</p>', 1, 1, 60, '2019-11-03', '/img/217/543731.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3780, 'The Idea of North', 35, '<p>Lyra arrives to her new life in London, determined to find Roger with Mrs Coulter\'s help. The Gyptians continue their search for the missing children and the elusive Gobblers.</p>', 2, 1, 60, '2019-11-10', '/img/222/555290.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3781, 'The Spies', 35, '<p>From the clutches of the Gobblers, Lyra finds help from an unlikely place. It helps her put together more about her past and keep safe from Mrs Coulter and the Magisterium.</p>', 3, 1, 60, '2019-11-17', '/img/225/562774.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3782, 'Armour', 35, '<p>Lyra and the Gyptians arrive in the North and seek the help of the Witches\' Consul, Texan aeronaut Lee Scoresby and an armoured bear in service to the town.</p>', 4, 1, 60, '2019-11-24', '/img/225/562583.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3783, 'The Lost Boy', 35, '<p>The alethiometer sends Lyra and Iorek on a new path, leading to a shocking but vital clue in her search to find her friend Roger and the other missing children.</p>', 5, 1, 60, '2019-12-01', '/img/227/569624.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3784, 'The Daemon-Cages', 35, '<p>Lyra discovers the horrific truth behind the Gobbler\'s activities in the North. She must now use all her wits to help free those around her and avoid suffering a terrible fate.</p>', 6, 1, 60, '2019-12-08', '/img/229/573162.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3785, 'The Fight to the Death', 35, '<p>Separated from her friends, Lyra must use all of her methods of deception to thwart a formidable foe. Elsewhere, Mrs Coulter plots her next move.</p>', 7, 1, 60, '2019-12-15', '/img/229/573412.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
(3786, 'Betrayal', 35, '<p>As the Magisterium closes in, Lyra learns more about Asriel\'s rebellion. But her assistance to him comes at great personal cost...</p>', 8, 1, 60, '2019-12-22', '/img/229/573413.jpg', '2019-12-19 02:15:14', '2019-12-19 02:15:14'),
